a.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhamas-vows-full-force-after-israel-steps-up-gaza-ground-operations%2Famp_articleshow%2F104768504.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhamas-vows-full-force-after-israel-steps-up-gaza-ground-operations%2Famp_articleshow%2F104768504.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Expands%20Ground%20Raids%2C%20Internet%20Services%20Cut%20Off%20Across%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20series%20of%20strikes%20of%20the%20last%20days%2C%20the%20ground%20forces%20are%20extending%20the%20ground%20operation%20tonight%2C%26quot%3B%20announced%20military%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari%20yesterday%20after%20two%20straight%20nights%20of%20tank%20incursions%20into%20Gaza.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas%20has%20vowed%20to%20confront%20the%20attacks%20with%20%26quot%3Bfull%20force%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Al-Qassam%20brigades%20and%20all%20the%20Palestinian%20resistance%20forces%20are%20completely%20ready%20to%20confront%20(Israel's)%20aggression%20with%20full%20force%20and%20frustrate%20its%20incursions%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20today.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsrael%20has%20unleashed%20one%20of%20its%20fiercest%20bombardments%20in%20Gaza%2C%20cutting%20off%20phone%20and%20internet%20links%20across%20the%20strip.%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%2C%20an%20NGO%2C%20has%20expressed%20concern%20that%20a%20communication%20blackout%20amid%20fierce%20bombardment%20in%20Gaza%20risks%20providing%20cover%20for%20mass%20atrocities.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas%20said%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bcut%20communications%20and%20most%20of%20the%20internet%26quot%3B%20across%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20accused%20them%20of%20taking%20the%20measure%20%26quot%3Bto%20perpetrate%20massacres%20with%20bloody%20retaliatory%20strikes%20from%20the%20air%2C%20land%20and%20sea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsrael%20has%20accused%20the%20Hamas%20group%20of%20using%20Gaza's%20biggest%20hospital%20as%20its%20headquar