20to%20escalate%2C%20intensify%20the%20war%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmirabdollahian%20spoke%20less%20than%20a%20day%20after%20the%20US%20said%20that%20it%20had%20conducted%20military%20strikes%20on%20two%20Syrian%20facilities%20linked%20to%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20that%20had%20been%20used%20for%20attacks%20against%20US%20troops%20in%20the%20region.%20US%20officials%20have%20said%20they%20don't%20have%20evidence%20that%20Iran%20explicitly%20ordered%20those%20attacks%20but%20they%20hold%20Iran%20responsible%20because%20it%20supports%20groups%20that%20carried%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20groups%20attacking%20US%20forces%20in%20Syria%20and%20Iraq%20are%20acting%20independently%2C%20and%20haven't%20received%20direction%20from%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20receiving%20any%20orders%20from%20us%2C%20any%20instructions%2C%26quot%3B%20Amirabdollahian%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20American%20side%20claims%20that%20these%20are%20linked%20to%20Iran.%20These%20groups%20decide%20for%20themselves%20independently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAttention%20has%20also%20focused%20on%20the%20possible%20outcome%20if%20Israel%20proceeds%20with%20a%20full%20ground%20invasion%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20root%20out%20Hamas%20after%20an%20Oct.%207%20raid%20by%20the%20group%2C%20which%20is%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%20Airstrikes%20of%20Gaza%20have%20already%20killed%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%20and%20on%20Friday%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20passed%20a%20resolution%20calling%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWestern%20officials%20have%20worried%20that%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20fighters%20in%20Lebanon%20would%20launch%20a%20barrage%20of%20attacks%20that%20could%20overwhelm%20Israeli%20air%20defenses.%20On%20Friday%2C%20US%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20said%20the%20US%20has%20voiced%20its%20conc