22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fpakistan-cricketers-left-heartbroken-after-failed-drs-appeal-vs-south-africa-in-cricket-world-cup-2023-watch-4521614%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Abstains%20From%20UN%20Vote%20On%20Israel%20Which%20Didn't%20Mention%20Hamas%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20abstained%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20on%20a%20resolution%20that%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20truce%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20leading%20to%20a%20cessation%20of%20hostilities.%20It%20also%20called%20for%20unhindered%20humanitarian%20access%20in%20the%20Gaza%20strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20launched%20a%20massive%20counter-offensive%20against%20Hamas%20after%20unprecedented%20attacks%20by%20the%20militant%20group%20on%20October%207%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20193%20members%20of%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20(UNGA)%2C%20which%20met%20in%20a%20resumed%2010th%20Emergency%20Special%20Session%2C%20voted%20on%20the%20draft%20resolution%20submitted%20by%20Jordan%20and%20co-sponsored%20by%20more%20than%2040%20nations%20including%20Bangladesh%2C%20Maldives%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Russia%20and%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20titled%20%26quot%3BProtection%20of%20civilians%20and%20upholding%20legal%20and%20humanitarian%20obligations%26quot%3B%20was%20adopted%20with%20120%20nations%20voting%20in%20its%20favour%2C%2014%20against%20it%20and%2045%20abstaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20India%2C%20countries%20that%20abstained%20included%20Australia%2C%20Canada%2C%20Germany%2C%20Japan%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Jordanian-drafted%20resolution%20did%20not%20make%20any%20mention%20of%20the%20militant%20group%20Hamas%2C%20with%20the%20US%20expressing%20outrage%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bomission%20of%20evil%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20general%20assembly%20voted%20on%20the%20resolution%2C%20the%20193-member%20body%20considered%20an%20amendment%20proposed%20by%20Canada%20and%20co-sponsored%20by%20the%20US%20to%20the%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20amendment%20proposed%20by%20Canada%20asked%20for%20inserting%20a%20paragraph%20in%20the%20resolution%20that%20would%20state%20that%20the%20general%20assembly%20%26quot%3Bunequivocally%20rejects%20and%20condemns%20the%20terrorist%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Israel%20starting%20on%207%20October%202023%20and%20the%20taking%20of%20hostages%2C%20demands%20the%20safety%2C%20well-being%20and%20humane%20treatment%20of%20the%20hostages%20in%20compliance%20with%20international%20law%2C%20and%20calls%20for%20their%20immediate%20and%20unconditional%20release%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20amendment%20along%20with%2087%20other%20nations%2C%20while%2055%20member%20states%20voted%20against%20it%20and%2023%20abstained.%20The%20draft%20amendment%20could%20not%20be%20adopted%2C%20having%20failed%20to%20obtain%20a%20two-third%20majority%20of%20members%20present%20and%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresident%20of%20the%2078th%20session%20of%20the%20UNGA%2C%20Dennis%20Francis%2C%20announced%20that%20the%20draft%20amendment%20could%20not%20be%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Jordanian-drafted%20resolution%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%2C%20durable%20and%20sustained%20humanitarian%20truce%20leading%20to%20a%20cessation%20of%20hostilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20demanded%20the%20immediate%2C%20continuous%2C%20sufficient%20and%20unhindered%20provision%20of%20essential%20goods%20and%20services%20to%20civilians%20throughout%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20water%2C%20food%2C%20medical%20supplies%2C%20fuel%20and%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20resolution%20stressed%20the%20imperative%2C%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20of%20ensuring%20that%20civilians%20are%20not%20deprived%20of%20objects%20indispensable%20to%20their%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%2C%20full%2C%20sustained%2C%20safe%20and%20unhindered%20humanitarian%20access%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20United%20Nations%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%20Refugees%20in%20the%20Near%20East%20and%20other%20United%20Nations%20humanitarian%20agencies%20and%20their%20implementing%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20resolution%20also%20demanded%20humanitarian%20access%20for%20the%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%20and%20all%20other%20humanitarian%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20should%20be%20done%20by%20upholding%20humanitarian%20principles%20and%20delivering%20urgent%20assistance%20to%20civilians%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20encouraging%20the%20establishment%20of%20humanitarian%20corridors%20and%20other%20initiatives%20to%20facilitate%20the%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20the%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20expressed%20outrage%20at%20the%20resolution%20not%20naming%20Hamas%20and%20called%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bomission%20of%20evil%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you'll%20notice%2C%20two%20key%20words%20are%20missing%20in%20the%20resolution%20before%20us.%20The%20first%20is%20Hamas.%20It%20is%20outrageous%20that%20this%20resolution%20fails%20to%20name%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20October%207th%20terrorist%20attacks%3A%20Hamas.%20Hamas.%20It%20is%20outrageous%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20the%20UN%20Linda%20Thomas-Greenfield%2C%20in%20her%20remarks%20before%20the%20vote%20on%20the%20resolution%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20another%20key%20word%20missing%20in%20the%20resolution%20is%20%26quot%3Bhostage%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20resolution%20makes%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20innocent%20people%20%E2%80%93%20including%20citizens%20of%20many%20of%20you%20in%20this%20room%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20you%20here%20today%20who%20have%20citizens%20who%20are%20being%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20and%20other%20terrorist%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20omissions%20of%20evil.%20And%20they%20give%20cover%20to%2C%20and%20they%20empower%2C%20Hamas'%20brutality.%20And%20no%20member%20state%20%E2%80%93%20no%20member%20state%20%E2%80%93%20should%20allow%20that%20to%20happen.%20You%20should%20not%20let%20it%20stand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20envoy%20said%20it%20is%20for%20these%20reasons%20that%20Washington%20has%20co-sponsored%20an%20amendment%20put%20forward%20by%20Canada%20to%20the%20draft%20resolution%20%26quot%3Bthat%20corrects%20these%20glaring%20omissions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20demanded%20that%20all%20parties%20immediately%20and%20fully%20comply%20with%20their%20obligations%20under%20international%20law%2C%20including%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20and%20international%20human%20rights%20law%2C%20particularly%20in%20regard%20to%20the%20protection%20of%20civilians%20and%20civilian%20objects%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20protection%20of%20humanitarian%20personnel%20and%20to%20facilitate%20humanitarian%20access%20for%20essential%20supplies%20and%20services%20to%20reach%20all%20civilians%20in%20need%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20called%20for%20the%20rescinding%20of%20the%20order%20by%20%26quot%3BIsrael%2C%20the%20occupying%20power%2C%20for%20Palestinian%20civilians%20and%20United%20Nations%20staff%2C%20as%20well%20as%20humanitarian%20and%20medical%20workers%2C%20to%20evacuate%20all%20areas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20north%20of%20the%20Wadi%20Gaza%20and%20relocate%20to%20southern%20Gaza.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20called%20for%20the%20immediate%20and%20unconditional%20release%20of%20all%20civilians%20who%20are%20being%20illegally%20held%20captive%2C%20demanding%20their%20safety%2C%20well-being%20and%20humane%20treatment%20in%20compliance%20with%20international%20law.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698460620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2F66f21f4_un-general-assembly_625x300_28_September_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-abstains-from-un-vote-on-israel-which-doesnt-mention-hamas-attack-4521836%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20abstained%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20on%20a%20resolution%20that%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20truce%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20leading%20to%20a%20cessation%20of%20hostilities.%20It%20also%20called%20for%20unhindered%20humanitarian%20access%20in%20the%20Gaza%20strip.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-abstains-from-un-vote-on-israel-which-doesnt-mention-hamas-attack-4521836%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-abstains-from-un-vote-on-israel-which-doesnt-mention-hamas-attack-4521836%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-abstains-from-un-vote-on-israel-which-doesnt-mention-hamas-attack-4521836%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHad%20He%20Given%20It%20Out...%26quot%3B%3A%20Babar's%20Honest%20Verdict%20On%20Crucial%20DRS%20Decision%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20disappointed%20Pakistan%20captain%20Babar%20Azam%20took%20it%20on%20his%20stride%20despite%20being%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20a%20DRS%20call%20during%20his%20team's%20gut-wrenching%20one-wicket%20loss%20to%20South%20Africa%20in%20a%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20match%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Friday.%20It%20could%20have%20been%20all%20over%20in%20the%2046th%20over%20for%20South%20Africa%20when%20a%20Haris%20Rauf%20delivery%2C%20bowled%20wide%20off%20the%20crease%2C%20stuck%20Keshav%20Maharaj%20on%20the%20pads%20and%20Pakistan%20went%20for%20the%20DRS%20call%20after%20on-field%20umpire%20ruled%20it%20not%20out.%20Ball%20tracking%20showed%20that%20the%20ball%20would%20have%20kissed%20the%20leg%20stump%20but%20Maharaj%20survived%20the%20DRS%20appeal%2C%20courtesy%20Umpires'%20Call%2C%20leaving%20the%20entire%20Pakistan%20unit%20distraught.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20This%20is%20umpire's%20call%20so%20I%20think%20it's%20just%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20Had%20he%20given%20it%20out%2C%20it%20would%20have%20favoured%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Babar%20said%20during%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20DRS%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Pakistan%20almost%20out%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20Babar%20seemed%20drained%20with%20the%20opportunity%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20disappointing%20everyone%2C%20we%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20win%20this%20match%20and%20stay%20in%20the%20tournament%20but%20we%20missed%20it.%20We%20will%20try%20our%20best%20in%20our%20next%20three%20matches%20and%20put%20our%20effort%20so%20let's%20see%20where%20we%20stand%20after%20the%20three%20matches.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBabar%20blamed%20his%20batters%20for%20falling%2020%20runs%20short%20what%20could%20have%20been%20a%20winning%20score%20on%20the%20Chepauk%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20disappointing%2C%20we%20fought%20back%20well%20but%20we%20were%2010-15%20runs%20short.%20I%20think%20the%20way%20fast%20bowlers%20bowled%2C%20they%20did%20well%20but%20unfortunately%20the%20result%20was%20not%20in%20our%20side.%26quot%3B%20South%20Africa%20captain%20Temba%20Bavuma%20didn't%20mince%20words%20while%20pointing%20out%20that%20they%20need%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20losing%20close%20games%20and%20was%20glad