PORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fnba%2Ftop-stories%2Fnba-denver-nuggets-outshoot-memphis-grizzlies-in-a-three-point-duel%2Farticleshow%2F104768200.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Man%20Jailed%20For%2016%20Years%20For%20Raping%20College%20Student%20In%20Singapore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20court%20in%20Singapore%20has%20sentenced%20a%2026-year-old%20Indian%20national%20to%2016%20years'%20jail%20and%2012%20strokes%20of%20the%20cane%20for%20raping%20a%20university%20student%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20took%20charges%20of%20kidnapping%20and%20theft%20into%20consideration%20for%20the%20sentencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20TODAY%20newspaper%20reported%20that%20after%20stalking%20the%20university%20student%20as%20she%20walked%20to%20a%20bus%20stop%20late%20at%20night%2C%20Chinnaiah%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20cleaner%2C%20pointed%20her%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction%20and%20then%20punched%20her%20before%20dragging%20her%20to%20a%20forested%20area%20and%20raping%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20so%20badly%20injured%20with%20facial%20bruising%20and%20other%20injuries%20that%20her%20then%20boyfriend%20did%20not%20recognise%20her%20upon%20visiting%20her%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rape%20took%20place%20on%20May%204%2C%202019.%20The%20court%20heard%20that%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20case%20had%20taken%20some%20four%20years%20to%20get%20to%20it%20was%20that%20Chinnaiah's%20mental%20condition%20had%20required%20several%20rounds%20of%20psychiatric%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Public%20Prosecutor%20(DPP)%20Kayal%20Pillay%20said%20that%20while%20Chinnaiah%20was%20sexually%20assaulting%20the%20student%2C%20she%20had%20tried%20to%20pull%20his%20hand%20away%20from%20her%20throat%20as%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20breathe.%20But%20Chinnaiah%20responded%20by%20tightening%20his%20grip%2C%20causing%20her%20to%20wheeze%20further%2C%20Mr%20Pillay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20told%20her%20to%20keep%20quiet%20and%20that%20no%20one%20would%20hear%20her.%20Mr%20Pillay%20said%20that%20after%20he%20raped%20her%2C%20Chinnaiah%20started%20rummaging%20through%20her%20belongings.%20He%20took%20her%20water%20bottle%20and%20drank%20from%20it%20before%20he%20poured%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20water%20over%20the%20lower%20half%20of%20her%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20he%20walked%20away%2C%20the%20student%20immediately%20went%20to%20her%20bag%20where%20she%20found%20her%20scissors%20and%20held%20them%20in%20her%20hand%20in%20case%20Chinnaiah%20returned%2C%20The%20DPP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20locate%20her%20spectacles%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20find%20her%20mobile%20phone%20to%20speak%20to%20her%20boyfriend.%20He%20later%20contacted%20her%20friend%20who%20called%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20DPP%20said%20after%20police%20arrived%2C%20the%20student%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20for%20a%20sexual%20assault%20examination%20where%20she%20was%20found%20to%20have%20sustained%20multiple%20scratches%2C%20bruises%20and%20scrapes%2C%20including%20strangulation%20marks%20over%20her%20neck%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChinnaiah%20was%20arrested%20on%20May%205%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeeking%2015%20to%2017%20years'%20jail%20and%2016%20to%2018%20strokes%20of%20the%20cane%2C%20the%20prosecution%20argued%20that%20the%20degree%20of%20violence%20used%20to%20facilitate%20the%20rape%20was%20extreme%20and%20his%20attack%20had%20been%20unrelenting%20and%20vicious.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDPP%20Yvonne%20Poon%20also%20said%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20not%20spur%20of%20the%20moment%20as%20Chinnaiah%20had%20numerous%20interactions%20with%20the%20victim%20and%20had%20directed%20her%20away%20from%20her%20last%20possible%20route%20to%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20Chinnaiah's%20pre-meditation%20as%20%26quot%3Binsidious%26quot%3B%2C%20DPP%20Poon%20added%20that%20the%20man%20had%20made%20serious%20efforts%20to%20avoid%20detection%20by%20making%20his%20presence%20less%20apparent%20as%20he%20followed%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20DPP%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20university%20student's%20victim%20impact%20statement%20dated%20July%2013%2C%202023%2C%20where%20she%20states%20she%20still%20has%20nightmares%20and%20flashbacks%2C%20thoughts%20of%20suicide%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20shame.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20aggravated%20rape%2C%20Chinnaiah%20could%20have%20been%20jailed%20for%20up%20to%2020%20years%20with%20no%20fewer%20than%2012%20strokes%20of%20the%20cane.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698459120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Fjustice-generic-court-generic_650x400_61513069872.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-man-jailed-for-16-years-for-raping-college-student-in-singapore-4521869%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20court%20in%20Singapore%20has%20sentenced%20a%2026-year-old%20Indian%20national%20to%2016%20years'%20jail%20and%2012%20strokes%20of%20the%20cane%20for%20raping%20a%20university%20student%20in%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-man-jailed-for-16-years-for-raping-college-student-in-singapore-4521869%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-man-jailed-for-16-years-for-raping-college-student-in-singapore-4521869%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-man-jailed-for-16-years-for-raping-college-student-in-singapore-4521869%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Mass%20Shooter%20Who%20Killed%2018%20Found%20Dead%20After%202%20Days%20Of%20Deadly%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect%20in%20a%20mass%20shooting%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Maine%20has%20been%20found%20dead%20of%20an%20apparent%20self-inflicted%20gunshot%20wound%2C%20US%20media%20reported%20Friday%2C%20after%20an%20intense%20manhunt%20that%20lasted%20more%20than%20two%20days.%20Confirmed%20details%20were%20not%20immediately%20known%2C%20but%20authorities%20in%20Maine%20called%20a%20news%20conference%20for%2010%20pm%20(0200%20GMT).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECNN%20reported%20that%20the%20body%20of%20Robert%20Card%2C%2040%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwill-never-feel-safe-us-city-deserted-as-cops-hunt-for-killer-4517913%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esubject%20of%20a%20massive%20manhunt%20following%20a%20rampage%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20days%20earlier%20that%20left%2018%20people%20dead%2C%20was%20found%20in%20woods%20about%20eight%20miles%20from%20Lewiston.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20network%20said%20Card's%20body%20was%20discovered%20near%20a%20recycling%20center%2C%20from%20which%20he%20had%20recently%20been%20fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECNN%20and%20ABC%20cited%20sources%20saying%20Card%20had%20been%20found%20dead%20of%20an%20apparent%20self-inflicted%20gunshot%20wound.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECard%20is%20accused%20of%20carrying%20out%20the%20country's%20deadliest%20mass%20shooting%20of%20the%20year%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20fatalities%2C%20another%2013%20people%20were%20wounded%20in%20the%20bloodshed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20on%20Friday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmaine-lewiston-shooting-a-father-and-teen-son-out-for-bowling-night-among-us-shooting-victims-4518117%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentified%20the%20victims%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ranging%20from%20a%20husband%20and%20wife%20in%20their%2070s%2C%20to%20a%2014-year-old%20boy%20k