e%2C%20ethnicity%2C%20sexual%20preference%20or%20political%20affiliation%20find%20their%20story%20reflected%20in%20the%20polarised%20and%20partisan%20account%20likely%20to%20be%20constructed%20for%20Yug%20Yugeen%20Bharat%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20final%20and%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20most%20difficult%20issue%20is%20that%20the%20very%20historicality%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20its%20journey%20through%20recorded%20time%2C%20and%20its%20emergence%20as%20a%20modern%20nation%20through%20actual%20events%20%E2%80%93%20is%2C%20under%20the%20current%20regime%2C%20sought%20to%20be%20muddied%20with%20terminology%20like%20%E2%80%9CYug%20Yugeen%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CAmrit%20Kaal%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20conjuring%20up%20fuzzy%20notions%20of%20timelessness%2C%20eternity%2C%20immortality%2C%20and%20perfection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20conflicts%20and%20struggles%20of%20real%20people%20in%20empirically%20verifiable%20contexts%20vanish%20under%20these%20vague%20fictions%20of%20an%20unchanging%20and%20unproblematic%20%E2%80%9CBharat%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20has%20no%20beginning%20and%20no%20end%2C%20whether%20temporal%20or%20spatial.%20If%20our%20government%20is%20going%20to%20resort%20to%20anachronistic%20and%20obfuscatory%20language%2C%20edit%20and%20erase%20troublesome%20facts%2C%20ignore%20whole%20communities%20and%20sideline%20entire%20cultures%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20their%20demographic%20dimensions%3B%20if%20it%20is%20going%20to%20project%20an%20imaginary%20%E2%80%9CAmrit%20Kaal%E2%80%9D%20nowhere%20in%20evidence%20while%20ignoring%20the%20devastating%20%E2%80%9CAapad%20Kaal%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20how%20are%20we%20supposed%20to%20trust%20it%20to%20make%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20best%20museum%20for%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fthe-demolition-of-the-national-museum-will-ex