0addition%20to%20the%20attacks%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20ground%20forces%20are%20expanding%20their%20operations%20tonight%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20military%20spokesman%20Rear%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said%20in%20a%20televised%20news%20briefing%20on%20Friday%20evening%2C%20raising%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20a%20long-anticipated%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20may%20be%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Israel's%20air%20force%20was%20conducting%20extensive%20strikes%20on%20tunnels%20dug%20by%20Hamas%20and%20other%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20armed%20wing%20of%20Hamas%20said%20late%20on%20Friday%20its%20fighters%20were%20clashing%20with%20Israeli%20troops%20in%20Gaza's%20northeastern%20town%20of%20Beit%20Hanoun%20and%20in%20the%20central%20area%20of%20Al-Bureij.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Al-Qassam%20brigades%20and%20all%20the%20Palestinian%20resistance%20forces%20are%20completely%20ready%20to%20confront%20(Israel's)%20aggression%20with%20full%20force%20and%20frustrate%20its%20incursions%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamas%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20early%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNetanyahu%20and%20his%20defeated%20army%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20achieve%20any%20military%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20the%20Israeli%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20ground%20forces%20had%20massed%20outside%20Gaza%2C%20where%20Israel%20has%20been%20conducting%20an%20intense%20campaign%20of%20aerial%20bombardment%20since%20a%20deadly%20Oct.%207%20attack%20by%20hundreds%20of%20Hamas%20gunmen%20on%20Israeli%20communities%20near%20the%20strip.%20Israel%20says%201%2C400%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20were%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20200%20taken%20hostage%2C%20some%20of%20them%20foreign%20nationals%20or%20with%20dual%20Israeli%20nationality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAl%20Jazeera%2C%20which%20was%20broadcasting%20live%20footage%20overnight%20showing%20frequent%20blasts%20in%20Gaza%2C%20said%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20had%20hit%20areas%20around%20the%20enclave's%20main%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReuters%20was%20unable%20to%20verify%20the%20reports%20of%20the%20strikes%20near%20Al%20Shifa%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20accused%20Hamas%20on%20Friday%20of%20using%20the%20hospital%20as%20a%20shield%20for%20its%20tunnels%20and%20operational%20centres%2C%20an%20allegation%20the%20group%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUN%20ASSEMBLY%20BACKS%20CALL%20FOR%20HUMANITARIAN%20TRUCE%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20overwhelmingly%20backed%20a%20resolution%20drafted%20by%20Arab%20states%20calling%20for%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20truce%20and%20demanded%20aid%20access%20to%20Gaza%20and%20protection%20of%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20binding%2C%20the%20resolution%20carries%20political%20weight%2C%20reflecting%20the%20global%20mood.%20It%20passed%20to%20a%20round%20of%20applause%20with%20121%20votes%20in%20favour%2C%20while%2044%20abstained%20and%2014%20-%20including%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20States%20-%20voted%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Israel%20announced%20a%20step-up%20in%20operations%2C%20White%20House%20national%20security%20spokesperson%20John%20Kirby%20said%20the%20U.S.%20did%20support%20a%20pause%20in%20Israeli%20military%20activity%20in%20Gaza%20to%20get%20humanitarian%20aid%2C%20fuel%20and%20electricity%20to%20civilians%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKirby%20would%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20expanded%20ground%20operation.%20But%20he%20said%20Washington%20supported%20Israel's%20right%20to%20defend%20itself%20and%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20drawing%20red%20lines%20for%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKirby%20also%20said%20that%20if%20getting%20more%20than%20200%20hostages%20abducted%20by%20Hamas%20out%20of%20Gaza%20required%20a%20localized%20temporary%20pause%2C%20then%20the%20U.S.%20supported%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%2C%20telecoms%20firms%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20Red%20Crescent%20Society%20said%20internet%20and%20phone%20services%20were%20cut%20off%20as%20a%20result%20of%20Israeli%20bombardments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E'BLACKED%20OUT'%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGaza%20is%20currently%20blacked%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paltel%2C%20the%20largest%20telecommunications%20provider%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Red%20Crescent%20Society%20said%20it%20had%20completely%20lost%20contact%20with%20its%20Gaza%20operations%20room%20and%20its%20teams%20operating%20there%2C%20and%20the%20Hamas-run%20government%20said%20rescue%20crews%20were%20unable%20to%20receive%20emergency%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMedecins%20Sans%20Frontieres%20(Doctors%20Without%20Borders)%20said%20it%20had%20been%20unable%20to%20reach%20some%20Palestinian%20colleagues%2C%20and%20said%20it%20was%20particularly%20worried%20for%20%26quot%3Bpatients%2C%20medical%20staff%20and%20thousands%20of%20families%20taking%20shelter%20at%20Al%20Shifa%20hospital%20and%20other%20health%20facilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20head%20of%20the%20U.N.%20Children's%20Fund%20UNICEF%2C%20Catherine%20Russell%2C%20said%20her%20agency%20too%20could%20no%20longer%20communicate%20with%20staff%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20extremely%20concerned%20about%20their%20safety%20and%20another%20night%20of%20unspeakable%20horror%20for%201M%20children%20in%20%23Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BAll%20humanitarians%20and%20the%20children%20and%20families%20they%20serve%20MUST%20be%20protected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMark%20Regev%2C%20an%20adviser%20to%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20told%20MSNBC%20that%20Israel%20was%20starting%20its%20payback%20against%20Hamas%20and%20%26quot%3BGaza%20will%20feel%20our%20wrath%20tonight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20our%20military%20blows%20until%20we%20have%20dismantled%20their%20military%20machine%20and%20dissolve%20their%20political%20structure%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Fox%20News.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20this%20is%20over%2C%20Gaza%20will%20be%20very%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20leaders%20have%20vowed%20to%20wipe%20out%20Hamas%20and%20kill%20the%20leaders%20and%20planners%20of%20the%20Oct.%207%20assault%20that%20surprised%20and%20shocked%20Israel.%20Israel%20has%20said%20it%20is%20preparing%20a%20ground%20invasion%2C%20but%20has%20been%20urged%20by%20the%20U.S.%20and%20Arab%20countries%20to%20delay%20an%20operation%20that%20would%20multiply%20the%20number%20of%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20the%20densely%20populated%20coastal%20strip%20and%20might%20ignite%20a%20wider%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20backed%20by%20Israel's%20main%20regional%20enemy%20Iran%2C%20has%20had%20years%20to%20prepare%20its%20defences.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20Israel%20has%20uncovered%20a%20sophisticated%20network%20of%20tunnels%20and%20Hamas%20has%20fired%20missiles%20at%20Israel%20since%20launching%20this%20month's%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20health%20authorities%20say%20Israeli%20bombing%20has%20already%20killed%20more%20than%207%2C000%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20a%20risk%20of%20a%20wider%20Middle%20East%20conflict%20have%20risen%20in%20recent%20days%20with%20the%20U.S.%20dispatching%20more%20military%20assets%20to%20the%20region%20as%20Israel%20pummelled%20targets%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Hamas%20supporters%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20of%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20been%20living%20under%20blockade%20by%20Israel%20and%20Egypt%20since%202007%2C%20has%20been%20shattered%20by%20Israeli%20bombing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPower%20has%20been%20cut%20for%20days%2C%20crippling%20treatment%20facilities%20and%20depriving%20Gazans%20of%20fresh%20water%2C%20while%20half%20of%20its%20housing%20stock%20has%20been%20damaged%20and%2020%2C000%20residential%20units%20destroyed%20or%20rendered%20uninhabitable%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas%20media%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPalestinians%20said%20they%20received%20renewed%20Israeli%20military%20warnings%20to%20move%20from%20Gaza's%20north%20to%20the%20south%20to%20avoid%20the%20deadliest%20theatre%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaking%20the%20journey%20south%20remains%20highly%20risky%20amid%20air%20strikes%20and%20southern%20areas%20have%20also%20been%20bombed%2C%20Gaza%20residents%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20families%20have%20refused%20to%20leave%2C%20fearing%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20experience%20of%20previous%20wars%20with%20Israel%20when%20Palestinians%20who%20left%20their%20homes%20and%20land%20were%20never%20able%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698455040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F255eis3_israel-gaza-reuters_625x300_11_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-vows-full-force-after-israel-steps-up-gaza-ground-operations-4521840%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hamas%20said%20on%20Saturday%20its%20militants%20in%20Gaza%20were%20ready%20to%20confront%20Israeli%20attacks%20with%20%26quot%3Bfull%20force%26quot%3B%20after%20Israel's%20military%20widened%20its%20air%20and%20ground%20attacks%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20enclave.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-vows-full-force-after-israel-steps-up-gaza-ground-operations-4521840%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-vows-full-force-after-israel-steps-up-gaza-ground-operations-4521840%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n