%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried%20testified%20before%20the%20jury%20on%20Friday%2C%20detailing%20his%20version%20of%20events.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20alarmed%20by%20Alameda%20Research's%20risks%20and%20lack%20of%20hedging.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20doesn't%20show%20it%20when%20he's%C2%A0%26quot%3Bfreaking%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20contrary%20to%20testimony%20by%20former%20execs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried%20took%20the%20stand%20on%20Friday%20to%20tell%20a%20jury%20his%20side%20of%20the%20story%20of%20how%20his%20cryptocurrency%20empire%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rare%20move%20for%20the%20defendant%20comes%20after%20he%20spent%20weeks%20listening%20to%20his%20inner%20circle%2C%20several%20of%20whom%20have%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20financial%20crimes%2C%20describe%20their%20version%20of%20events.%20(A%20prosecutor%20even%20accused%20Bankman-Fried%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-laughed-shook-head-caroline-ellison-testimony-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshaking%20his%20head%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20the%20testimony%2C%20though%20former%20CEO's%20attorney%20denied%20it.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20stand%20before%20the%20jury%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20described%20learning%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-trial-adam-yedidia-bug-8-billion-alameda-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%248%20billion%20hole%20in%20the%20finances%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20his%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%2C%20FTX%2C%20in%20mid-2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20have%20alleged%20the%20hole%20came%20about%20after%20Bankman-Fried%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-sbf-fraud-trial-ftx-explainer-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efunneled%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20customer%20funds%20from%20FTX%20to%20Alameda%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EResearch%2C%20his%20crypto%20trading%20firm%2C%20and%20then%20loaned%20the%20money%20to%20himself%20and%20his%20fellow%20executives.%20They%20have%20charged%20him%20with%20seven%20financial%20crimes%2C%20including%20fraud%20and%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202022%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bnervous%26quot%3B%20Caroline%20Ellison%20alerted%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20along%20with%20FTX%20executives%20Gary%20Wang%20and%20Nishad%20Singh%2C%20that%20she%20was%20concerned%20Alameda%20may%20have%20just%20gone%20bankrupt.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%20a%20co-CEO%20of%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20surprised%20and%20fairly%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20testified.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20not%20expected%20that%20Alameda%20would%20be%20bankrupt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison's%20assessment%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20a%20tumultuous%20summer%20in%20the%20crypto%20market%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202022%2C%20but%20Bankman-Fried%20didn't%20think%20Alameda's%20assets%20on%20FTX%20had%20fluctuated%20enough%20for%20the%20firm%20he%20founded%20in%202017%20to%20go%20bankrupt%2C%20he%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20investigating%2C%20Wang%20and%20Singh%20informed%20Bankman-Fried%20that%20there%20was%20a%20bug%20in%20FTX's%20code%20that%20caused%20a%20miscalculation%20of%20%248%20billion%2C%20suggesting%20that%20Alameda's%20balance%20was%20actually%20positive.%20Developers%20ran%20the%20numbers%20and%20confirmed%20them%2C%20bringing%20about%20a%20%26quot%3Brelieved%26quot%3B%20demeanor%20in%20Ellison%2C%20Singh%2C%20and%20Wang%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20they%20believed%20a%20crisis%20had%20been%20averted%2C%20the%20situation%20did%20cause%20Bankman-Fried%20to%20consider%20shuttering%20Alameda%20altogether%20as%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bfairly%20concerned%20about%20Alameda's%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%20didn't%20want%20to%20shut%20down%