ion%20and%20gender%20identity%20in%20early%20grades.%20The%20law%20was%20championed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-desantis-feud-court-filing-park-wants-damages-contract-2023-8%5C%22%3EDeSantis%2C%20who%20currently%20is%20running%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20the%202024%20GOP%20presidential%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20control%20of%20the%20district%20changed%20hands%20from%20Disney%20allies%20to%20DeSantis%20appointees%2C%20the%20Disney%20supporters%20on%20its%20board%20signed%20agreements%20with%20Disney%20shifting%20control%20over%20design%20and%20construction%20at%20Disney%20World%20to%20the%20company%20and%20prohibiting%20the%20district%20from%20using%20the%20likeness%20of%20Disney%20characters%20or%20other%20intellectual%20property%20without%20Disney's%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20DeSantis%20appointees%20claimed%20the%20%26quot%3Beleventh-hour%20deals%26quot%3B%20neutered%20their%20powers%2C%20and%20the%20district%20sued%20the%20company%20in%20state%20court%20to%20have%20the%20contracts%20voided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20has%20filed%20counterclaims%20which%20include%20asking%20the%20state%20court%20to%20declare%20the%20agreements%20valid%20and%20enforceable.%20Disney%20also%20is%20seeking%20from%20DeSantis'%20office%20and%20several%20state%20agencies%20internal%20communications%2C%20including%20text%20messages%2C%20emails%2C%20and%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProductions%20to%20date%20have%20been%20nonexistent%20or%20woefully%20deficient%2C%26quot%3B%20Disney%20said%20in%20its%20court%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20and%20DeSantis%20and%20his%20allies%20also%20are%20battling%20in%20federal%20court%2C%20where%20the%20company%20has%20sued%20DeSantis%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fdisney-desantis-florida-lgbtq-theme-park-c6e20b56fbf68f9bda1dadeed2284120%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclaiming%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20governor%20vi