.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20freewheeling%20discussion%2C%20Mr%20Doshi%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20UK%20emerging%20as%20a%20top%20destination%20for%20Indian%20students%20and%20how%20he%20has%20been%20telling%20students%20to%20come%20back%20and%20work%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhappening%20place%26quot%3B%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGiven%20the%20current%20India-Canada%20face-off%20and%20the%20diplomatic%20spat%2C%20will%20going%20to%20Canada%20for%20higher%20studies%20be%20difficult%20for%20Indian%20students%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20put%20things%20in%20perspective.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20Canada%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20you%20have%20seen%20an%20exponential%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20students%20applying%20to%20Canada.%20Why%20is%20that%3F%201)%20It%20is%20a%20very%20friendly%20nation.%20They%20welcome%20you%20with%20open%20arms.%202)%20There%20are%20lots%20of%20facilities%20for%20research%20and%20extracurricular%20activities.%203)%20Job%20opportunities%20are%20tremendous%3B%20and%20the%20fourth%20attraction%20is%20to%20get%20that%20permanent%20residence%20to%20settle%20down%20in%20Canada.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Canada%20has%20become%20a%20very%20popular%20destination%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20lately%2C%20because%20of%20the%20political%20fallout%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20been%20asking%20me%20what%20is%20going%20to%20happen%20in%20Canada%3F%20I%20still%20believe%20it's%20a%20hiccup.%20I%20think%20things%20will%20improve.%20If%20I%20talk%20to%20students%20at%20the%20ground%20level%20in%20Canada%2C%20they%20are%20extremely%20happy.%20The%20political%20fallout%20has%20not%20impacted%20them%20at%20all.%20I%20think%20we%20read%20more%20about%20it%20in%20our%20papers%20out%20here%2C%20so%20we%20feel%20that%20the%20impact%20is%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20answering%20your%20question%2C%20as%20students%20are%20now%20getting%20ready%20to%20apply%20for%20next%20year%2C%20there%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20apprehension.%20Parents%20and%20students%20both%20are%20concerned%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20-%20will%20the%20visa%20come%20on%20time%2C%20will%20we%20get%20there%2C%20will%20our%20children%20be%20welcomed%20out%20there%2C%20will%20we%20get%20a%20job%20after%20that%20or%20not%3F%20These%20are%20apprehensions.%20I%20think%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20all%20these%20apprehensions%2C%20people%20are%20still%20applying.%20There%20may%20be%20a%20slight%20drop%20in%20applications%2C%20but%20people%20are%20still%20applying%20because%20Canada%20is%20a%20very%20favoured%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20they%20are%20going%20to%20do%20is%20they%20are%20going%20to%20apply.%20There%20may%20be%20a%20small%20drop%2C%20but%20they%20will%20%C2%A0have%20a%20wait-and%20watch%20attitude.%20And%2C%20sometime%20by%20May-June%2C%20when%20the%20decisions%20come%20out%20and%20they%20see%20what%20the%20political%20scenario%20is%2C%20I%20think%20then%20they%20will%20take%20this%20issue.%20But%20I%20don't%20see%20a%20major%20drop%20in%20applications%20to%20Canada%20at%20all.%20I%20think%2C%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20people%20will%20still%20apply%20to%20Canada%2C%20and%20I%20think%20who%20we%20must%20give%20credit%20to%20are%20the%20Canadian%20universities.%20The%20admission%20directors%20have%20really%20reached%20out%20to%20students%20and%20parents%2C%20both%20through%20emails%20and%20seminars%2C%20and%20made%20them%20very%20comfortable.%20(They%20have%20said)%20%26quot%3BLook%20here%2C%20this%20is%20a%20hiccup.%20It's%20not%20impacting%20college%20life%20at%20all.%20So%20please%20do%20apply%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20think%20parents%20eventually%20want%20an%20assurance.%20That%20assurance%20is%20coming%20from%20the%20Canadian%20colleges.%20So%20I%20really%2C%20honestly%2C%20don't%20feel%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20too%20much%20of%20a%20change%2C%20believe%20me.%20But%20yes%2C%20people%20will%20talk%20about%20it%20in%20the%20cocktail%20circuit%20-%20What%20should%20we%20do%3F%20What%20we%20shouldn't%20do.%20But%2C%20eventually%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20applications%2C%20people%20will%20still%20apply%20but%20have%20a%20wait-and-watch%20attitude%20and%20see%20whether%20the%20visas%20are%20coming%20on%20time.%20If%20they%20do%20get%20the%20visas%2C%20they%20will%20definitely%20be%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%2C%20if%20not%20Canada%2C%20then%20where%20else%20for%20Indian%20students%3F%20We%20know%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Australia%20are%20popular%20choices.%20But%20do%20you%20see%20students%20branching%20out%20beyond%20these%20options%20to%2C%20let's%20say%2C%20Europe%20and%20other%20countries%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20look%20at%20overseas%20education%2C%20I%20would%20say%20between%20USA%2C%20Canada%20and%20UK%2C%20they%20must%20be%20taking%2090%25%20of%20students%20who%20are%20going%20overseas%20today%2C%20and%20the%20balance%2010%25%20would%20have%20gone%20to%20Australia%2C%20maybe%20to%20Europe%2C%20to%20Singapore%2C%20to%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20to%20Dubai.%20But%20still%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20things%20are%20not%20going%20to%20change%20so%20rapidly%20that%20people%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20other%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20yes%2C%20people%20are%20looking%20at%20other%20countries.%20To%20some%20extent%2C%20Europe%20is%20getting%20a%20little%20more%20popular%20right%20now%20because%20of%20the%20cost.%20(It's)%20Very%20friendly.%20But%20Europe%20has%20its%20disadvantages%20of%20being%20a%20little%20more%20insular.%20In%20colleges%20you%20study%20in%20English%2C%20but%20outside%20it's%20in%20a%20foreign%20language.%20The%20networking%20in%20European%20colleges%20has%20become%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20challenge%20because%2C%20again%2C%20it's%20populated%20with%20the%20local%20population%20out%20there.%20That%20does%20become%20a%20challenge.%20And%20eventually%2C%20when%20you%20go%20to%20college%2C%20you%20also%20go%20for%20the%20networking%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%20You%20also%20go%20for%20the%20whole%20atmosphere%20out%20there.%20This%20is%20sometimes%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20challenge%20in%20the%20European%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Europe%2C%20Netherlands%20is%20becoming%20quite%20popular.%20France%20is%20also%20getting%20out%20there.%20Germany%2C%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20do%20technical%20education%2C%20is%20looking%20quite%20popular.%20But%20it's%20not%20really%20exponentially%20increased%20(like)%20what%20you%20see%20in%20other%20countries.%20Today%2C%20when%20you%20tell%20me%20you%20want%20to%20go%20overseas...%20As%20I%20said%2C%2090%25%20will%20go%20to%20USA%2C%20Canada%20and%20UK.%20And%20if%20students%20will%20not%20go%20to%20Canada%2C%20they%20will%20look%20at%20UK%20as%20a%20very%20serious%20option%20for%20two%20reasons%20-%20in%20UK%20the%20cost%20is%20as%20much%20as%20Canada%2C%20it's%20not%20as%20expensive%20as%20America%3B%20you%20finish%20in%20three%20years%20and%20the%20job%20placements%20in%20UK%20are%20fabulous%20now.%20I%20think%20the%20whole%20scenario%20has%20changed%20with%20the%20new%20visa%20regime.%20So%20UK%20is%20going%20to%20become%20a%20very%20strong%20destination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUSA%20will%20increase%2C%20but%20education%20in%20the%20USA%20is%20very%20expensive%20in%20the%20private%20colleges.%20But%20there%20will%20be%20an%20increase%20in%20US%20admissions%20also.%20People%20are%20going%20to%20play%20safe%20now.%20They%20will%20apply%20to%20Canada.%20They%20will%20also%20apply%20to%20colleges%20in%20the%20USA%20and%20UK%20and%20a%20few%20of%20them%20will%20also%20apply%20to%20colleges%20in%20Singapore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingapore%20is%20a%20good%20destination%20to%20go%20to%2C%20but%20the%20challenge%20in%20Singapore%20is%20you%20have%20limited%20colleges.%20You've%20got%20SMU%20(Singapore%20Management%20University)%2C%20NUS%20(National%20University%20of%20Singapore)%20and%20NTU%20(Nanyang%20Technological%20University).%20So%20not%20too%20many%20choices%20out%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20Europe%20does%20become%20a%20destination.%20But%2C%20when%20I%20say%20Europe%2C%20actually%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20more%20of%20UK.%20UK%20will%20definitely%20see%20a%20substantial%20increase%20in%20applicants%20applying%20out%20there.%20Because%20of%20the%20%C2%A0positive%20impact%20of%20the%20visa%20regime%20out%20there%2C%20more%20and%20more%20people%20have%20been%20looking%20at%20UK%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20which%20was%20not%20the%20case%20before%20the%20new%20visa%20regime%20set%20in.%20So%20I%20don't%20think%20new%20countries...%20they%20will%20see%20an%20upsurge%2C%20but%20not%20as%20substantial%20as%20the%20UK%20will%20see%20and%20Canada%20will%20see.%20But%2C%20believe%20me%2C%20Canada%20will%20not%20have%20a%20drop%20in%20applications.%20It'll%20be%20a%20wait-and%20watch%20review%20and%20take%20a%20decision%20by%20next%20June%2C%20July.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20students%20already%20in%20Canada%2C%20what's%20next%3F%20You%20have%20already%20mentioned%20that%20this%20diplomatic%20row%20has%20not%20penetrated%20classrooms%2C%20thankfully.%20Is%20it%20going%20to%20be%20difficult%20for%20Indians%20to%20get%20jobs%20in%20Canada%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20this%20is%20something%20that%20we%20feel%2C%20in%20our%20minds%2C%20that%20this%20is%20going%20to%20impact%20us.%20I%20think%20that%20Canadians%20have%20not%20taken%20this...%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20political%20situation%20has%20impacted%20recruitment%20out%20there%20because%20they%20all%20know%20the%20Indian%20students%20are%20hardworking.%20Academically%20they%20have%20been%20very%20strong%2C%20so%20they%20do%20become%20an%20attraction%20for%20every%20company.%20So%2C%20I%20honestly%20don't%20believe%20this%20political%20fallout%20will%20impact%20employment%20at%20all.%20And%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20companies%20even%20go%20down%20to%20that%20level%20to%20say%20%26quot%3Boh%2C%20because%20of%20this%20fallout%20we%20will%20not%20take%20you%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20think%20Canadians%20are%20very%20magnanimous.%20If%20you%20look%20at...%20just%20remove%20the%20political%20fallout%2C%20I%20think%20students%20will%20always%20be%20welcomed%20out%20there.%20They%20will%20be%20very%20happy%20out%20there.%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20job%20placements%20will%20be%20impacted.%20It's%20all%20in%20our%20minds%20right%20now.%20I%20think%20as%20things%20settle%20down%2C%20people%20will%20see%20that%2C%20really%2C%20it%20does%20not%20impact%20employment%20at%20all.%20It%20will%20not%20impact%20employment.%20%C2%A0Because%20Canadians%20are%20very%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20go%20to%20Canada%2C%20you%20will%20see%20how%20fair%20they%20are%2C%20how%20welcoming%20they%20are.%20Even%20today%2C%20I%20had%20somebody%20visiting%20Canada%20who%20said%20it's%20just%20normal.%20Nothing%20has%20happened.%20Nothing%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20ground%20reality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFurther%20clearing%20the%20air%20around%20the%20ground%20reality%20in%20Canada%2C%20should%20students%20in%20Canada%20apply%20elsewhere%20for%20jobs%20after%20they%20finish%20their%20studies%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%20where%3F%20You%20require%20visas%20to%20study%20in%20any%20country%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%20So%20you%20are%20not%20going%20to%20get%20a%20visa%20to%20USA%20or%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20go%20and%20work%20out%20there.%20Honestly%2C%20I've%20been%20telling%20students%20for%20the%20last%20year%20or%20two%20to%20come%20back%20to%20India.%20You%20can't%20get%20a%20better%20place%20than%20India.%20Why%20should%20they%20work%20anywhere%20else%3F%20India%20is%20a%20happening%20place%20today.%20This%20is%20a%20place%20for%20students%20to%20come%20back%20to.%20And%20if%20you%20really%20want%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Canada%2C%20maybe%20work%20for%20a%20year%20or%20two%20out%20here%20and%20go%20back%20for%20your%20post-graduate%20degree%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHopefully%2C%20by%20then%2C%20the%20situation%20will%20be%20much%20better%2C%20I'm%20sure.%20And%20you'll%20get%20the%20job%20that%20you%20want%2C%20eventually%2C%20out%20there.%20So%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20should%20be%20a%20knee-jerk%20reaction.%20Jobs%20will%20be%20good%20out%20there.%20And%2C%20if%20they%20don't%2C%20come%20back%20to%20India%2C%20young%20people%2C%20this%20is%20where%20the%20action%20is%20for%20the%20next%2010-15%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20do%20you%20think%20employers%20often%20look%20favourably%20at%20candidates%20who%20have%20completed%20their%20education%20at%20prestigious%20institutions%20abroad%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20at%20all.%20I%20think%20Indian%20colleges%20have%20come%20of%20age.%20Look%20at%20the%20marvellous%20colleges%20that%20we%20have%20in%20this%20country.%20From%20Ashoka...%20to%20NMIMS%20(Narsee%20Monjee%20Institute%20of%20Management%20Studies).%20They're%20fabulous.%20And%20IIMs%20and%20IITs.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20ask%20any%20recruiter%20in%20this%20country%2C%20given%20a%20choice...%20if%20you%20have%20two%20students%2C%20one%20with%20an%20overseas%20education%20and%20one%20from%20India%2C%20they%20will%20always%20prefer%20the%20Indian%20one.%20Why%3F%20They%20are%20more%20adaptable.%20They%20are%20more%20malleable%20and%20they%20are%20able%20to%20fit%20into%20the%20whole%20working%20system%20out%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20that's%20why%20when%20students%20go%20abroad%2C%20I%20tell%20them%20go%20there%20for%20the%20education.%20Don't%20think%20you'll%20have%20any%20distinct%20advantage%20when%20you%20come%20back%20to%20this%20country.%20Yes%2C%20you'll%20have%20a%20good%20education%2C%20but%20you'll%20be%20on%20a%20par%20with%20any%20other%20student%20who%20has%20gone%20to%20a%20good%20Indian%20university.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20advantage%20of%20going%20abroad%20which%20was%20there%20maybe%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20think%20with%20the%20coming%20of%20age%20of%20our%20education%20system%2C%20I%20think%20they%20will%20be%20on%20a%20par%20or...%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20slight%2055-45%20preference%20to%20Indian%20students.%20Talk%20to%20recruiters%2C%20they%20will%20tell%20you%20the%20same%20thing%2C%20they%20will%20prefer%20a%20student%20from%20here%20than%20one%20who%20has%20gone%20overseas.%20But%20going%20overseas%20is%20not%20necessary%20to%20have%20an%20advantage%20out%20here.%20It's%20for%20the%20education%2C%20the%20overall%20holistic%20education%20that%20you%20get%20when%20you%20go%20overseas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWell%2C%20Mr%20Doshi%2C%20your%20parting%20short%20for%20all%20those%20students%20who%20may%20be%20interested%20in%20or%20prepping%20their%20college%20applications%20to%20study%20abroad%20this%20year%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%20keep%20your%20doors%20open.%20Don't%20restrict%20yourself%20to%20one%20particular%20country.%20Let's%20see%20how%20things%20evolve.%20Canada%20will%20not%20change.%20It%20will%20be%20the%20same%20as%20it%20was%20before.%20Please%20apply%20everywhere.%20Keep%20your%20doors%20open%20and%20take%20a%20call%20sometime%20in%20April-May%20next%20year%2C%20when%20the%20situation%2C%20hopefully%2C%20will%20improve%20and%20you%20get%20all%20the%20results%20coming%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698433920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fd49l92eo_viral-doshi-650_625x300_28_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcanada-to-be-top-destination-for-indian-students-despite-row-expert-to-ndtv-4521649%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Friday%2C%20leading%20educational%20consultant%20Viral%20Doshi%20said%20that%20despite%20the%20apprehensions%20following%20the%20India-Canada%20diplomatic%20row%2C%20Canada%20will%20remain%20a%20preferr