t%3D%5C%221772%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDielle%20Charon%2C%20a%20sales%20coach.%3Cp%3EDanielle%20Riley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EStarting%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20can%20be%20a%20heavy%20lift%20but%20can%20have%20big%20marketing%20benefits.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ETo%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20it%2C%20optimize%20it%20for%20customer%20questions%20and%20search-engine%20optimization.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EDelegate%20the%20more%20technical%20aspects%2C%20and%20monetize%20your%20videos%20to%20offset%20costs%2C%20if%20possible.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarketing-for-small-business%5C%22%3EMarketing%20for%20Small%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20exploring%20the%20basics%20of%20marketing%20strategy%20for%20SBOs%20to%20earn%20new%20customers%20and%20grow%20their%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20Mariah%20Liszewski%2C%20a%20search-engine%20optimization%20consultant%2C%20started%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40MariahMagazine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20her%20business%2C%20Mariah%20Magazine%2C%20she%20burned%20out%20after%20a%20few%20dozen%20videos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20exhausting%20process%20of%20learning%20all%20the%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20including%20microphones%20and%20editing%20software%20%E2%80%94%20she%20wasn't%20using%20her%20videos%20strategically%20or%20seeing%20a%20return%20on%20her%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20until%202021%2C%20when%20she%20made%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdPYx-eS4gyE%26t%3D23s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20video%20about%20Google's%20new%20analytics%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20response%20to%20client%20questions%20about%20it%20and%20published%20it%20on%20YouTube.%20The%20video%20went%20viral%20(it%20has%20over%2047%2C000%20views)%2C%20which%20inspired%20Liszewski%20to%20rethink%20her%20YouTube%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20she's%20found%20a%20way%20to%20make%20it%20work%20for%20her%20%E2%80%94%20and%20her%20business.%20Liszewski%20now%20publishes%20just%20two%20videos%20a%20month%20and%20has%20seen%20YouTube%20become%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20sources%20of%20organic%20traffic%20to%20her%20website%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20more%20email%20subscribers%2C%20digital-product%20purchases%2C%20and%20leads%20for%20SEO%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22499%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Mariah%20Liszewski%2C%20who%20is%20wearing%20glasses%20and%20a%20denim%20jacket.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65393c600487ff031cae02c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22374%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMariah%20Liszewski%2C%20a%20consultant%20for%20search-engine%20optimization.%3Cp%3EMariah%20Magazine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20favorite%20thing%20about%20the%20platform%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20that%20videos%20can%20keep%20getting%20traction%20for%20months%20or%20years%2C%20making%20YouTube%20a%20more%20sustainable%20marketing%20channel%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20the%20pressure%20off%20of%20having%20to%20consistently%20create%20content%20for%20the%20faster-moving%20platforms%20like%20Instagram%20or%20TikTok%2C%26quot%3B%20Liszewski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDielle%20Charon%2C%20a%20sales%20coach%20who%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40diellecharon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20YouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year%20and%20has%20grown%20to%20over%20500%20subscribers%20in%20eight%20months%2C%20agreed%20that%20YouTube%20had%20been%20an%20evergreen%20way%20to%20grow%20her%20email%20list.%20It%20has%20allowed%20customers%20to%20connect%20with%20her%20and%20help%20them%20convert%20to%20her%20high-ticket%20offers%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20chatted%20with%20Liszewski%20and%20Charon%20about%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20use%20YouTube%20to%20market%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EChoose%20topics%20that%20are%20easy%20for%20you%20and%20compelling%20to%20your%20customers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECharon%20said%20she'd%20found%20success%20by%20choosing%20basic%20topics%20for%20her%20videos.%20These%20are%20not%20only%20easy%20for%20her%20to%20talk%20about%20(meaning%20less%20work%20has%20to%20go%20into%20scripting)%20but%20also%20ideal%20for%20the%20YouTube%20audience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20beginners%20on%20YouTube%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20why%20they're%20searching%2C%20because%20they%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Charon%20said.%20She%20discourages%20founders%20from%20putting%20out%20advanced%20content.%20She's%20found%20that%20basic%20%26quot%3Bhow-to%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bdos%20and%20don'ts%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcommon%20mistakes%26quot%3B%20videos%20do%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20valuable%20way%20to%20plan%20YouTube%20content%20is%20based%20on%20the%20questions%20your%20clients%20%E2%80%94%20or%20viewers%20in%20the%20comments%20of%20your%20other%20videos%20%E2%80%94%20are%20asking%20you.%20%26quot%3BMy%20clients%20joke%20around%20that%20if%20you%20have%20a%20question%2C%20I've%20probably%20got%20a%20YouTube%20video%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Liszewski%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Liszewski%20encourages%20founders%20to%20choose%20topics%20that%20feel%20fun%20to%20create%20versus%20thinking%20soley%20about%20the%20strategy%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20burnout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMaximize%20the%20SEO%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20grow%20your%20YouTube%20channel%20%E2%80%94%20and%20business%20%E2%80%94%20is%20to%20tap%20into%20its%20SEO%20potential.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20search%20for%20a%20sales%20coach%20or%20business%20coach%20or%20my%20name%2C%20YouTube%20videos%20come%20up%2C%20and%20they%20can%20really%20see%20me%20in%20action%20and%20know%20if%20I'm%20the%20coach%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Charon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiszewski%20also%20makes%20sure%20to%20maximize%20the%20search%20potential%20of%20each%20video.%20Once%20she%20brainstorms%20video%20ideas%20based%20on%20her%20interests%20and%20audience%20questions%2C%20she'll%20run%20them%20through%20an%20SEO%20tool%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tubebuddy.com%2Ftools%2Fkeyword-explorer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETubeBuddy%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20see%20whether%20there%20are%20any%20keywords%20she%20can%20target%20that%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20she%20makes%20sure%20to%20say%20the%20keyword%20throughout%20her%20video.%20Since%20YouTube%20automatically%20transcribes%20videos%2C%20the%20algorithm%20picks%20up%20on%20the%20words%20that%20she's%20saying.%20Liszewski%20also%20mentions%20the%20keyword%20in%20the%20title%20and%20video%20description%20and%20adds%20tags%20with%20the%20keyword%20to%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20going%20to%20YouTube%20to%20search%20for%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Liszewski%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20you%20show%20up%20and%20be%20the%20best%20solution%20to%20that%20problem%3F%20We%20essentially%20have%20to%20give%20the%20YouTube%20algorithm%20context%20clues%20about%20what%20this%20video%20is%20about.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMonetize%20if%20you%20can%2C%20but%20don't%20make%20that%20the%20goal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELiszewski%20said%20things%20really%20changed%20for%20her%20when%20she%20reached%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fyoutube%2Fanswer%2F72851%3Fhl%3Den%26co%3DGENIE.Platform%253DAndroid%23%3A~%3Atext%3D