22summary%22%3A%22Two%20major%20Palestinian%20mobile%20networks%20%E2%80%93%20Jawwal%20and%20Paltel%20%E2%80%93%20said%20their%20phone%20lines%20and%20internet%20services%20have%20been%20cut%20off.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcomplete-black-out-in-gaza-as-mobile-internet-services-cut-off-by-israeli-bombing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22He%20Asked%20If%20He%20Should%20%26quot%3BShoot%26quot%3B%20Himself%3A%20Wife%20Of%20Ex%20Railway%20Cop%20Who%20Killed%204%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMoments%20after%20allegedly%20gunning%20down%20four%20persons%20in%20a%20train%20near%20Mumbai%2C%20including%20a%20senior%20colleague%2C%20dismissed%20Railway%20Protection%20Force%20(RPF)%20constable%20Chetansinh%20Chaudhary%20called%20up%20his%20wife%20and%20said%20he%20had%20committed%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20mistake%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20her%20if%20he%20should%20%26quot%3Bshoot%26quot%3B%20himself%2C%20too%2C%20according%20to%20her%20statement%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20case's%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChetansinh%20Chaudhary's%20wife%2C%20Priyanka%2C%20has%20made%20this%20claim%20in%20a%20statement%20given%20to%20the%20police%20after%20the%20July%20incident%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20chargesheet%20filed%20by%20the%20Government%20Railway%20Police%20(GRP)%2C%20the%20probe%20agency%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20statement%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bblood%20clot%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20brain%20and%20was%20taking%20medicines%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20GRP%20on%20October%2020%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20before%20a%20magistrate's%20court%20here%20against%20Chetan%20Chaudhary%20(34)%2C%20accused%20of%20fatally%20shooting%20a%20senior%20colleague%20and%20three%20passengers%20on%20board%20a%20moving%20Mumbai-bound%20express%20train%20on%20July%2031%20near%20Palghar%20railway%20station%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20metropolis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20booked%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20sections%20302%20(murder)%2C%20153-A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20residence%2C%20language%2C%20etc)%20and%20others%2C%20as%20well%20as%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20Railways%20Act%20and%20the%20Maharashtra%20Prevention%20Of%20Defacement%20of%20Property%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Chaudhary%2C%20in%20the%20statement%2C%20said%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20shooting%20incident%2C%20her%20husband%20phoned%20at%20around%206%3A30%20am%20and%20told%20her%20about%20his%20murderous%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMaine%20teen%20logon%20ko%2C%20aur%20ek%3C%2Fem%3E%20SI%20(sub-inspector)%20%3Cem%3Eko%20maar%20dia%20hai%E2%80%A6Mujse%20badi%20galti%20hogai%20hai..tum%20bolo%20toh%20apne%20AAP%20ko%20goli%20maar%20doon%20kya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%A6(I%20have%20killed%20three%20people%20and%20SI..%20Have%20made%20a%20big%20mistake%E2%80%A6shall%20I%20shoot%20myself%20too%3F)%2C%26quot%3B%20constable%20Chaudhary%20told%20his%20wife%2C%20according%20to%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20asked%20her%20husband%20to%20surrender%20before%20the%20police%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Chaudhary%20said%20her%20husband's%20father%2C%20who%20was%20also%20in%20the%20RPF%2C%20died%20on%20duty%20in%202007%20and%20Chetan%20Chaudhary%20was%20then%20studying%20in%20Class%2010.%20After%20completion%20of%2018%20years%2C%20Chetan%20Chaudhary%20joined%20the%20RPF%20on%20compensatory%20grounds%20and%20was%20posted%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20was%20transferred%20to%20Gujarat%20where%20he%20stayed%20in%20a%20village%20called%20Radavav%20near%20the%20coastal%20town%20of%20Porbandar.%20In%20April%20this%20year%2C%20the%20RPF%20constable%20was%20transferred%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Chaudhary%20told%20the%20police%20that%20when%20her%20mother-in-law%20went%20to%20meet%20Chetan%20Chaudhary%20in%20Porbandar%20in%20February%2C%20she%20found%20his%20%E2%80%9Cbehaviour%20abnormal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20her%20mother-in-law%2C%20the%20RPF%20constable%20used%20to%20suddenly%20start%20blabbering%2C%20something%20without%20any%20provocation%2C%20and%20also%20used%20to%20bang%20his%20head%20against%20the%20wall%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2013%20this%20year%2C%20Chetan%20Chaudhary%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20neurosurgeon%20in%20Mathura%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20After%20initial%20tests%20and%20MRI%20(magnetic%20resonance%20imaging)%2C%20it%20was%20diagnosed%20that%20there%20was%20a%20minor%20blood%20clotting%20in%20his%20brain%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%20the%20doctor%20gave%20him%20medicines%20for%20ten%20days.%20After%20the%20first%20course%2C%20when%20the%20doctor%20re-examined%20him%2C%20he%20found%20some%20improvement%20in%20his%20condition.%20Hence%2C%20he%20was%20advised%20to%20continue%20the%20same%20medications.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChetan%20Chaudhary's%20uncle%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20police%2C%20said%20the%20accused%20was%20disturbed%20because%20he%20was%20transferred%20from%20Porbandar%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20whereas%20he%20wanted%20posting%20in%20either%20Mathura%20or%20Agra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20has%20statements%20of%20several%20witnesses%2C%20including%20co-passengers%20of%20the%20Jaipur-Mumbai%20Central%20Express%2C%20where%20the%20gruesome%20incident%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2034-year-old%20RPF%20constable%20was%20caught%20with%20his%20weapon%20after%20passengers%20pulled%20the%20chain%20of%20the%20train%20which%20stopped%20near%20Mira%20Road%20station%20(on%20the%20Mumbai%20suburban%20network).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20shot%20dead%20RPF%20Assistant%20Sub-Inspector%20Tika%20Ram%20Meena%2C%20who%20was%20travelling%20with%20him%20in%20the%20train%2C%20and%20a%20passenger%20in%20B5%20coach%20with%20his%20automatic%20weapon%2C%20according%20to%20the%20GRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChetansinh%20Chaudhary%20then%20killed%20another%20passenger%20in%20the%20pantry%20car%20and%20one%20more%20traveller%20in%20S6%20coach%20next%20to%20the%20pantry%20car%20after%205%20am%2C%20said%20the%20probe%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20lawyer%20Amit%20Mishra%20said%20they%20will%20comment%20on%20the%20chargesheet%20only%20after%20going%20through%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698430320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fcmla8ki_rpf-constable-chetan-singh-1200_650x400_31_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrain-shooting-rpf-constable-he-asked-if-he-should-shoot-himself-wife-of-ex-railway-cop-who-killed-4-4521493%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Moments%20after%20allegedly%20gunning%20down%20four%20persons%20in%20a%20train%20near%20Mumbai%2C%20including%20a%20senior%20colleague%2C%20dismissed%20Railway%20Protection%20Force%20(RPF)%20constable%20Chetansinh%20Chaudhary%20called%20up%20his%20wife%20and%20said%20he%20had%20committed%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20mistake%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrain-shooting-rpf-constable-he-asked-if-he-should-shoot-himself-wife-of-ex-railway-cop-who-killed-4-4521493%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrain-shooting-rpf-constable-he-asked-if-he-should-shoot-himself-wife-of-ex-railway-cop-who-killed-4-4521493%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrain-