%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20court%20case%20also%20revealed%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20total%20amount%20Google%20paid%20in%202021%20to%20device-makers%2C%20including%20Apple%2C%20for%20default%20search-engine%20deals%20was%20an%20eye-watering%20%2426.3%20billion%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fleah_nylen%2Fstatus%2F1717932095685669234%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20Apple%20deal%20represented%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20that%20amount%2C%20and%20it%20just%20highlights%20how%20much%20Google%20is%20willing%20to%20pay%20to%20keep%20its%20search%20engine%20front%20and%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20does%20have%20its%20own%20search%20tool%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-spotlight-search-on-mac%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpotlight%3C%2Fa%3E%20feature%2C%20which%20is%20available%20to%20those%20with%20iPhones%2C%20iPads%2C%20and%20Mac%20computers.%20Spotlight%20is%20not%20a%20new%20concept%2C%20it's%20been%20on%20Apple%20devices%20since%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-should-kill-spotlight-search-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2005%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20considered%20a%20potential%20competitor%20to%20Google.%20The%20tool%20allows%20users%20to%20look%20up%20news%2C%20weather%2C%20and%20the%20meaning%20of%20words%20and%20phrases.%C2%A0%20The%20results%20look%20similar%20to%20those%20people%20could%20find%20on%20other%20search%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20competing%20with%20Apple%20on%20the%20search%20front%2C%20according%20to%20recent%20report%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2Ftechnology%2Fgoogle-apple-search-spotlight.html%3Fpartner%3Dslack%26smid%3Dsl-share%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20value%20of%20that%20privilege%20has%20ballooned%20considerably%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%20Back%20in%202014%2C%20Google%20paid%20Apple%20%241%20billion%20to%20stay%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-bargaining-power-over-google-search-mobile-safari-ios-2016-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%20devices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20court%20documents%20revealed%20in%20a%20separate%20case%20involving%20Oracle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Apple%20nor%20Google%20responded%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20ahead%20of%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Justice%20originally%20filed%20the%20suit%20against%20Google%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoj-google-antitrust-case-revealed-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2020%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20search%20engine%20was%20a%20monopoly%20that%20was%20hurting%20the%20ability%20of%20smaller%20companies%20to%20compete.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20trial%20is%20investigating%20Google's%20relationship%20with%20companies%20like%20Apple%20and%20device-makers%20running%20Android.%20The%20DOJ%20has%20argued%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-trial-expert-testifies-difficult-switch-default-search-engine-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20it%20intentionally%20difficult%20to%20switch%20from%20Google%20to%20other%20search%20engines%20on%20iPhones%20and%20Android%2C%20with%20a%20government%20witness%20testifying%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fgoogle-antitrust-trial-a2de0df014f7cfabdddd5aa3c19f12b9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20took%2010%20steps%20to%20