ransition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mohela.com%2Fsystem-transition%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweb%20page%20with%20information%20on%20the%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20impact%20the%20existing%20terms%2C%20conditions%2C%20interest%20rates%2C%20loan%20discharge%20or%20forgiveness%20programs%2C%20or%20available%20repayment%20plans%20on%20your%20loans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMOHELA%20borrowers%20will%20have%20to%20establish%20a%20new%20account%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20and%20its%20mobile%20app%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20available%20once%20the%20transition%20is%20complete.%20Additionally%2C%20if%20a%20borrower%20makes%20a%20payment%20to%20MOHELA%20that%20was%20not%20yet%20posted%20on%20their%20account%20prior%20to%20the%20transition%2C%20the%20payments%20%26quot%3Bmay%20be%20delayed%20by%20up%20to%2030%20business%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20guidance%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20will%20post%20the%20payment%20to%20your%20loan(s)%20with%20the%20effective%20date%20that%20the%20payment%20was%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20%26quot%3BPlease%20immediately%20begin%20using%20MOHELA's%20new%20contact%20information%20to%20make%20payments%20to%20avoid%20payment%20posting%20delays.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20affirmed%20in%20its%20guidance%20that%20aside%20from%20possible%20delays%2C%20borrowers%20should%20not%20suffer%20any%20other%20adverse%20effects%20from%20this%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20this%20change%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20month%20after%20federal%20student-loan%20payments%20resumed%20following%20an%20over%20three-year%20pause.%20To%20ease%20the%20transition%20back%20into%20repayment%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Education%20Department%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-best-way-to-pay-student-loan-debt-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E12-month%20%26quot%3Bon-ramp%