20by%20diesel%20engines%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Kishore%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698416996000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333114%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kolkata%20artist%20Kishore%20Pratim%20Biswas%20spent%2025%20dedicated%20years%20to%20a%20painting%20series%20on%20India's%20heritage%20steam%20trains.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333114%2Fkolkata-artist-kishore-pratim-biswas-paints-steam-locomotives%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%3A%20What%20Explains%20the%20Decline%20of%20BRS%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170220%2FF9XxRh3aQAA_Hcy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%2C%20formerly%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20is%20witnessing%20an%20unprecedented%20decline.%20Going%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fpolitics%2F201023%2Fsurvey-shows-congress-surge-in-telangana.html%5C%22%3Erecent%20surveys%3C%2Fa%3E%20ahead%20of%20the%20November%2030%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Congress%20is%20clearly%20on%20the%20ascendancy%20while%20the%20BRS%20is%20losing%20ground.%20Even%20if%20these%20surveys%20turn%20out%20modestly%20right%20and%20the%20BRS%20footprint%20declines%2C%20we%20need%20to%20look%20at%20the%20reasons%20closely%20not%20only%20to%20understand%20the%20developments%20in%20Telangana%20but%20also%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20general%20election%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETelangana%20was%20formed%20in%202014%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20at%20the%20Centre.%20BRS%20won%20the%20first%20and%20second%20assembly%20elections%20held%20in%20the%20new%20state%20due%20to%20the%20expansive%20transactional%20welfarism%20it%20rolled%20out%2C%20regional%20sentiment%2C%20relief%20from%20extreme%20drought%20conditions%20due%20to%20the%20digging%20of%20ponds%2C%20and%20laying%20new%20pipelines%20for%20the%20supply%20of%20drinking%20water.%20Further%2C%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20maintained%20a%20fair%20degree%20of%20communal%20harmony%20with%20special%20funds%20for%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20appointing%20a%20Muslim%20leader%20as%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20pitching%20for%2012%25%20reservations%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-brs-kcr-congress-bjp%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Polls%3A%20BRS%20Has%20Reason%20Not%20To%20Be%20Overconfident%20With%20Congress%20Poised%20To%20Challenge%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKCR%20brought%20in%20the%20unique%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme%20for%20landowning%20farmers%20by%20granting%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20acre%20twice%20a%20year%20in%20the%20form%20of%20investment%20support%20for%20agriculture.%20His%20government%20also%20announced%20the%20Dalit%20Bandhu%20scheme%2C%20which%20promised%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20Dalit%20families%20to%20help%20set%20up%20their%20own%20business%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20government%20has%20also%20started%20a%20Telangana%20Brahmin%20Samkshema%20Parishad%20to%20offer%20educational%20loans%20and%20support%20to%20Brahmin%20students%20who%20wish%20to%20pursue%20their%20higher%20education%20abroad.%20Since%20Telangana%20began%20as%20a%20state%20with%20a%20surplus%20budget%20in%202014%2C%20KCR%20rightly%20focused%20on%20welfare%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20bring%20about%20relief%20to%20most%20sections%20of%20the%20state%2C%20which%20faced%20neglect%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Andhra%20capitalists%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20united%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoss%20of%20direction%20in%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20second%20term%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20problems%20of%20misgovernance%20and%20a%20loss%20of%20direction%20have%20marked%20the%20second%20term%20of%20chief%20minister%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20(2018-present).%20Though%20his%20government%20still%20continues%20with%20many%20of%20its%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20visible%20change%20of%20mood%20in%20the%20state.%20Known%20for%20its%20social%20protest%20movements%2C%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20demography%20is%20dominated%20by%20Dalits%2C%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20and%20Muslims.%20Together%2C%20these%20groups%20constitute%2085%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%20It%20was%20movements%20led%20by%20each%20of%20these%20groups%20and%20their%20demands%20that%20gathered%20strength%20to%20culminate%20in%20articulating%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20state%20of%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKCR%20delivered%20on%20transactional%20welfarism%2C%20but%20also%20stoically%20neglected%20the%20aspirational%20demands%20rooted%20in%20the%20statehood%20movement%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98KG%20to%20PG%E2%80%99%20free%20education.%20He%20neglected%20higher%20education%20as%20he%20was%20upset%20over%20youth%20being%20part%20of%20many%20of%20the%20social%20mobilisations%20in%20the%20state.%20Universities%20in%20the%20state%20functioned%20without%20vice-chancellors%20for%20well%20over%20three%20years%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana%20in%202014.%20Many%20of%20these%20universities%20still%20continue%20to%20starve%20for%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENeglect%20of%20education%20has%20been%20coupled%20with%20the%20encouragement%20received%20by%20caste-based%20occupations%20through%20funds%20specifically%20given%20towards%20their%20modernisation.%20This%20presented%20a%20rather%20grim%20picture%20for%20the%20future%20of%20many%20Dalit-Bahujan%20castes.%20The%20BRS%20presented%20subsistence%20welfare%20but%20failed%20to%20fulfil%20aspirational%20imagination.%20The%20decline%20of%20BRS%20marks%20the%20shift%20from%20subsistence%20relief%20provided%20by%20patronage%20politics%20to%20aspirational%20politics%20based%20on%20self-respect%20and%20greater%20social%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20narrow%20and%20casteist%20vision%20of%20KCR%20is%20best%20represented%20in%20his%20own%20persona%2C%20which%20is%20abrasive%2C%20arrogant%2C%20and%20non-responsive.%20He%20emerged%20on%20the%20political%20scene%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20protest%2C%20but%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20manifested%20nothing%20but%20contempt%20for%20mass%20mobilisations.%20He%20also%20distanced%20himself%20from%20mass%20leaders%20of%20the%20statehood%20movement%20and%20got%20many%20of%20them%20arrested%2C%20including%20Kodandaram%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20chief%20of%20Telangana%20Jana%20Samithi.%20Recently%2C%20a%20case%20was%20framed%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Factivists-haragopal-sudha-bharadwaj-150-others-booked-under-uapa-last-august-accused-unaware%5C%22%3Ewell-known%20activists%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20to%20protests%20from%20various%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20popular%20anecdote%20among%20civil%20society%20activists%20in%20the%20state%20is%20that%20KCR%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20famous%20balladeer%20Gaddar%2C%20who%20waited%20for%20hours%20for%20an%20appointment.%20It%20is%20this%20arrogance%20of%20KCR%20that%20culminated%20in%20undermining%20the%20very%20regional%20sentiments%20that%20brought%20him%20to%20power.%20His%20aspiration%20to%20take%20his%20party%20national%20has%20also%20undermined%20legitimate%20regional%20sentiments.%20This%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20suicidal%20as%20there%20has%20been%20a%20loss%20of%20emotional%20connection%20with%20regional%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20failed%20attempts%20to%20emerge%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20BRS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20space%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20attempted%20to%20capture%20in%20Telangana.%20It%20attempted%20to%20communalise%20regional%20imagination.%20This%20did%20not%20work%20in%20Telangana%2C%20though%20it%20continues%20to%20have%20reasonable%20appeal%20among%20caste-Hindu%20middle%20classes.%20The%20BJP%20began%20to%20grow%20with%20great%20appeal%20among%20the%20OBCs.%20It%20then%20attempted%20to%20combine%20social%20justice%20with%20communal%20polarisation.%20Under%20the%20leadership%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funion-minister-kishan-reddy-made-telangana-bjp-chief-punjab-jharkhand-get-new-presidents%5C%22%3EBandi%20Sanjay%3C%2Fa%3E%20(who%20is%20from%20the%20OBC%20Munnuru%20Kapu%20community)%2C%20the%20BJP%20expanded%20its%20footprint.%20But%20Telangana%20has%20remained%20the%20land%20of%20Reddy%20domination%2C%20as%20Andhra%20is%20of%20the%20Kammas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-606011%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20Telangana%20unit%20president%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20BJP%20national%20executive%20meeting%20held%20on%20July%204%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20pursuing%20the%20policy%20of%20undermining%20independent%20leaders%20in%20states%2C%20following%20a%20clue%20from%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20brand%20of%20politics.%20They%20refuse%20to%20learn%20the%20lesson%20in%20a%20pitch%20to%20push%20for%20complete%20dependence%20on%20the%20manufactured%20charisma%20of%20Narendra%20Modi.%20They%20refuse%20to%20learn%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-cracks-appearing-in-bjps-telangana-unit-after-the-karnataka-debacle%5C%22%3Edebacle%20in%20Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20undermining%20Yeddyurappa%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%20staring%20at%20a%20steep%20challenge%20in%20Rajasthan%20after%20undermining%20the%20leadership%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-bjp-rebellion-first-list-publicly-opposed%5C%22%3EVasundhara%20Raje%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20wants%20to%20expand%20but%20with%20Modi%20as%20its%20only%20popular%20face.%20Beyond%20North%20and%20West%20India%2C%20Modi%20is%20not%20a%20leader%20with%20great%20reach%20in%20the%20South%20and%20the%20East.%20With%20the%20appointment%20of%20Union%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funion-minister-kishan-reddy-made-telangana-bjp-chief-punjab-jharkhand-get-new-presidents%5C%22%3EKishan%20Reddy%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Telangana%20BJP%20unit%20chief%20in%20the%20place%20of%20Bandi%20Sanjay%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20declined%20in%20terms%20of%20popular%20presence.%20Political%20pundits%20who%20were%20at%20one%20point%20predicting%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20BJP%20forming%20a%20government%20give%20them%20no%20more%20than%20five%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-telangana-polls-brs-kcr-rahul-gandhi%5C%22%3EFrom%20Pushover%20to%20Position%20of%20Strength%3A%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Gain%20Evident%20in%20Public%20Outcry%20Against%20BRS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevival%20of%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20perception%20among%20some%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20BRS%2C%20and%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20are%20working%20in%20tandem%20to%20arrest%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Congress.%20This%20has%20now%20made%20it%20a%20bipolar%20contest%20between%20Congress%20and%20the%20rest.%20The%20Congress%20has%20begun%20to%20articulate%20the%20new%20demands%20and%20regional%20aspirations%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20recent%20announcement%20that%20Kodandaram%2C%20a%20key%20leader%20of%20the%20statehood%20movement%20and%20the%20Telangana%20Jana%20Samithi%20chief%2C%20will%20work%20and%20contest%20together%20with%20the%20Congress%20has%20further%20helped%20the%20party%20capture%20the%20protest%20space%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170909%2FTelangana-Congress.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170909%2FTelangana-Congress.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170909%2FTelangana-Congress-300x207.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170909%2FTelangana-Congress-1024x706.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682103%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22827%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20and%20others%20during%20the%20election%20campaign%20in%20Telangana.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40RahulGandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20replication%20of%20the%20experiment%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20more%20than%20100%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcivil-society-organisations-played-key-role-in-congress-victory%2Farticle66846656.ece%5C%22%3Ecivil%20society%20organisations%3C%2Fa%3E%20worked%20independently%20but%20with%20a%20desire%20to%20keep%20out%20the%20BJP%2C%20in%20Telangana%20too%2C%20over%2050%20organisations%20came%20together%20under%20the%20platform%20of%20Telangana%20Vidhyavanthula%20Vedika%20to%20campaign%20independently%20against%20the%20misrule%20of%20the%20BRS%20and%20the%20danger%20posed%20by%20the%20BJP.%20These%20organisations%20have%20close%20grassroots%20connections%20in%20various%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKCR%20moved%20from%20being%20the%20poster%20boy%20of%20Telangana%20sensibilities%20and%20identity%20to%20betraying%20and%20undermining%20not%20only%20material%20mobility%20but%20psychological%20and%20emotional%20identification.%20This%20is%20akin%20to%20the%20terminal%20decline%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20when%20it%20turned%20against%20the%20peasants%20who%20were%20its%20mainstay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20increasingly%20occupying%20this%20space%20and%20filling%20the%20void%20both%20because%20of%20the%20favourable%20role%20it%20played%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20separate%20state%20through%20Sonal%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20and%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20presenting%20a%20left-of-centre%20vision.%20This%20shift%20is%20happening%20with%20scepticism%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20return%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Reddy%20landlordism%E2%80%99%20that%20Congress%20represented%20in%20the%20past%20in%20Telangana.%20If%20Congress%20maintains%20its%20transformative%20image%2C%20symbolism%2C%20and%20policy%20frame%2C%20it%20could%20look%20at%20a%20long%20haul%2C%20otherwise%2C%20people%20will%20move%20on%20to%20look%20for%20other%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmigrant-workers-middle-class-lockdown%5C%22%3EAjay%20Gudavarthy%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Political%20Studies%2C%20JNU.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698416945000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170220%2FF9XxRh3aQAA_Hcy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-what-explains-the-decline-of-brs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20state%20in%202014%2C%20the%20KCR%20government%20rightly%20focused%20on%20welfare.%20But%20recently%2C%20it%20is%20suffering%20because%20of%20alleged%20misgovernance%20and%20the%20perceived%20arrogance%20of%20KCR.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-what-explains-the-decline-of-brs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Parking%20Spot%3F%20Delhi%20Friends%20Are%20Using%20Tech%20to%20Make%20Parking%20Quick%2C%20Easy%20%26amp%3B%20Safe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20experiences%20immense%20joy%20when%20purchasing%20a%20car.%20Dhananjaya%20Bharadwaj%2C%20the%20former%20deputy%20commandant%20posted%20in%20Krishnapatnam%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332971%2Fbrillio-national-stem-learning-challenge-government-schools-rural-india-science-labs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20on%20cloud%20nine%20when%20he%20bought%20his%20BMW%20X1%20in%20October%202017.%20Wanting%20to%20share%20his%20excitement%2C%20he%20drove%20to%20Moradabad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20to%20take%20his%20mother%20on%20a%20ride%20in%20his%20shiny%20new%20SUV%20(sport%20utility%20vehicle).%20However%2C%20little%20did%20he%20anticipate%20that%20this%20journey%20from%20Moradabad%20to%20New%20Delhi%20would%20change%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20driving%20to%20Delhi%20for%20a%20family%20function%2C%20the%20duo%20headed%20to%20Karol%20Bagh.%20Dhananjaya%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20parking%20spot%20in%20the%20busy%20shopping%20area.%20After%20searching%20for%20more%20than%2020%20minutes%2C%20he%20eventually%20found%20a%20parking%20lot%20belonging%20to%20the%20North%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeeing%20the%20logo%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20it%20must%20be%20safe.%20The%20parking%20staff%20wanted%20me%20to%20leave%20the%20key.%20I%20was%20apprehensive%20but%20obliged%20after%20seeing%20that%20everyone%20was%20doing%20the%20same.%20I%20took%20my%20parking%20slip%20and%20left%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dhananjaya%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20two-hour%20shopping%20sojourn%2C%20what%20he%20saw%2C%20or%20rather%20didn%E2%80%99t%20see%2C%20made%20the%20ground%20beneath%20his%20feet%20sink.%20His%20car%20was%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen.%20When%20the%20staff%20there%20seemed%20indifferent%2C%20the%20former%20deputy%20commandant%20knew%20that%20%E2%80%9Csomething%20bad%20had%20happened%E2%80%9D.%20After%20some%20calls%20to%20the%20police%2C%20they%20found%20out%20that%20the%20car%20had%20been%20towed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20car%20was%20damaged%20and%20I%20had%20to%20pay%20more%20than%20Rs%201.75%20lakh%20to%20repair%20it.%20When%20I%20confronted%20the%20parking%20staff%2C%20they%20pointed%20me%20to%20these%20words%20on%20the%20parking%20slip%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98parking%20at%20owner%E2%80%99s%20risk%E2%80%99.%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20the%20only%20person%20facing%20this%20problem%20and%20harassment%20by%20the%20parking%20mafia%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2034-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConfronted%20with%20persistent%20parking%20issues%20in%20busy%20areas%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%20he%20spoke%20to%20his%20friend%20Abhimanyu%20Singh.%20This%20discussion%20spurred%20them%20to%20devise%20a%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20ParkMate.%20This%20app-based%20platform%20provides%20hyperlocal%20and%20on-demand%20parking%20solutions%20for%20businesses%20and%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolving%20the%20parking%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parkmate%20makes%20parking%20easier%20through%20technology%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333164%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParkmate%20offers%20a%20%E2%80%98Drop%20and%20Shop%E2%80%99%20service%20for%20customers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20article%20by%20The%20Patriot%2C%20Delhi%20alone%20witnesses%20approximately%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323849%2Fbengaluru-gagandeep-reehal-gursimran-kalra-ai-mobility-startup-built-zpod-driverless-car%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20crore%20cars%20%3C%2Fa%3Eparked%20daily%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20market%20worth%20Rs%2044.5%20crore.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20receives%20over%20250%20calls%20every%20day%2C%20concerning%20fights%20related%20to%20parking.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDhananjaya%20and%20Abhimanyu%2C%20who%20were%20both%20working%20with%20the%20Government%20at%20the%20time%2C%20decided%20to%20write%20a%20technical%20paper%20about%20the%20parking%20problem%20in%20the%20country.%20But%20their%20research%20led%20them%20to%20find%20a%20long-term%20viable%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%2097%20percent%20of%20this%20parking%20industry%20is%20unorganised.%20Traffic%20congestion%20leads%20to%20a%20Rs%201.45%20lakh%20crore-worth%20economic%20opportunity%20loss%20in%20four%20major%20cities%20of%20India.%20Of%20this%2C%20Rs%2036%2C000%20crore%20is%20due%20to%20parking%20congestion.%20A%20person%20burns%20100%20litres%20of%20fuel%20searching%20for%20parking%20daily%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dhananjaya%2C%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%2C%20ParkMate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20the%20data%2C%20the%20friends%20decided%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20themselves%20with%20ParkMate%2C%20which%20offers%20two%20solutions%20%E2%80%94%20DASH%20(Drop%20and%20Shop)%20for%20individuals%20and%20the%20Trident%20system%20for%20businesses%20for%20parking%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20access%20the%20DASH%20service%2C%20users%20can%20download%20the%20application%2C%20enter%20the%20destination%2C%20book%20a%20valet%2C%20and%20reach%20there.%20ParkMate%E2%80%99s%20attendants%2C%20who%20are%20OTP%20verified%2C%20will%20pick%20up%20the%20car%20from%20the%20set%20location.%20Dhananjaya%20says%20that%20all%20cars%20are%20GPS-tagged%2C%20enabling%20users%20to%20track%20their%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20live%20movement.%20They%20also%20share%20360-degree%20images%20of%20the%20cars%20before%20and%20after%20delivery%20with%20the%20customers.%20Once%20done%2C%20you%20can%20tap%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Get%20my%20car%E2%80%99%20option%20on%20the%20app%2C%20and%20collect%20the%20car%20wherever%20you%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20instant%2C%20safe%2C%20and%20guaranteed%20parking.%20At%20ParkMate%2C%20the%20risk%20is%20ours%2C%20not%20the%20owner%E2%80%99s.%20We%20cover%20all%20risks%20with%20five%20different%20kinds%20of%20insurance%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParkMate%20charges%20Rs%2049%20for%20its%20services%20plus%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330313%2Fnawgati-fuelling-management-app-innovative-startup-shark-tank-india-bits-pilani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparking%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20hire%20any%20staff%20on%20the%20ground%20but%20work%20with%20existing%20parking%20operators.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20with%20the%20official%20operators%20under%20a%20revenue-sharing%20model.%20We%20train%20the%20attendants%20for%2012%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20further%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20businesses%20like%20malls%2C%20shopping%20complexes%2C%20big%20residential%20societies%20and%20government%20offices%2C%20they%20offer%20a%20suite%20of%20software%20and%20hardware%20services%20to%20automate%20parking%20space%20through%20the%20Trident%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20system%20offers%20a%20three-tier%20integration%20of%20the%20FASTag%20plus%20ANPR%20(automatic%20number%20plate%20recognition)%20plus%20UniPay%20system%20(online%20payment%20for%20businesses)%2C%20which%20utilises%20state-of-the-art%20HD%20cameras%2C%20an%20inbuilt%20controller%2C%20and%20our%20proprietary%20software.%20Money%20is%20deducted%20through%20FASTag%20and%20license%20plates%20are%20scanned%20on%20entry%20and%20exit%2C%20making%20vehicle%20entry%20management%20effortless%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhimanyu%20Singh%2C%20co-founder%2C%20ParkMate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParkMate%E2%80%99s%20transactions%20are%20totally%20paperless.%20The%20founders%20say%20their%20goal%20is%20to%20reduce%20congestion%2C%20save%20fuel%2C%20and%20provide%20a%20hassle-free%20parking%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%20July%202022%2C%20ParkMate%20is%20present%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Jaipur%20and%20Lucknow.%20The%20duo%20share%20that%20they%20have%20served%20over%205.5%20lakh%20customers%20so%20far%2C%20and%20are%20launching%20their%20services%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20seven%20more%20cities%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20faced%20a%20frustrating%20time%20parking%20at%20Connaught%20Place%2C%20Karol%20Bagh%2C%20and%20other%20busy%20areas%20in%20Delhi.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20spent%20over%2015%20to%2020%20minutes%20every%20time%20just%20looking%20for%20a%20spot.%20Dealing%20with%20the%20staff%20on%20the%20ground%20is%20also%20a%20tough%20task.%20ParkMate%20has%20really%20simplified%20it%20and%20made%20my%20outings%20fun.%20Their%20interface%20is%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20smooth%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aditya%2C%20a%20ParkMate%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20a%20calculated%20risk%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ParkMate%20offer%20a%20Trident%20service%20for%20businesses%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333165%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParkMate%20offers%20a%20Trident%20service%20for%20businesses.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENurturing%20this%20idea%20since%202017%2C%20the%20pair%2C%20who%20initially%20met%20as%20teenagers%20at%20a%20Call%20of%20Duty%20(video%20game)%20World%20tournament%2C%20devoted%20time%20to%20refining%20their%20solution%20and%20saving%20funds%20before%20quitting%20their%20jobs.%20Coming%20from%20middle-class%20families%2C%20they%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20taking%20a%20calculated%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20hail%20from%20operational%20backgrounds.%20We%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20corpus%20that%20could%20sustain%20us%20for%20two%20years%20before%20leaving%20our%20jobs.%20Even%20then%2C%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20was%20not%20happy%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20me%20quitting%20my%20government%20job.%20We%20suffered%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAbba%20nahi%20maanenge%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Dad%20won%E2%80%99t%20agree)%20syndrome.%20My%20parents%20are%20still%20angry%2C%20but%20I%20know%20they%E2%80%99ll%20come%20around%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dhananjaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20say%20that%20they%20did%20not%20draw%20a%20salary%20for%20the%20first%2014%20months%2C%20and%20initially%2C%20they%20faced%20challenges%20in%20convincing%20customers%20and%20finding%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20industry%20is%20dominated%20by%20the%20mafia.%20It%E2%80%99s%20tough%20to%20approach%20them%20and%20seek%20a%20partnership.%20Moreover%2C%20we%20started%20our%20company%20during%20a%20funding%20winter%20(a%20time%20when%20venture%20capital%20was%20less)%20and%20had%20to%20pool%20in%20our%20own%20savings.%20The%20biggest%20challenge%20though%2C%20was%20educating%20people%20about%20our%20services%20and%20gaining%20their%20trust.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20advertisements%20for%20the%20same%20but%20have%20worked%20on%20building%20their%20trust%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dhananjaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20goal%20is%20now%20to%20expand%20across%20the%20country%20and%20become%20the%20go-to%20parking%20solution%20for%20Indians.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20anyone%20to%20worry%20about%20parking%20when%20they%20go%20out.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20have%20a%20good%20time.%20The%20risk%20is%20on%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Freports%2Fdelhis-mega-parking-crisis-10121%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Delhi%E2%80%99s%20mega%20parking%20crisis%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20Published%20on%2021%20June%2C%202019%20Courtesy%20The%20Patriot%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698416550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333159%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Based%20in%20Delhi%2C%20friends%20Dhananjaya%20Bharadwaj%20and%20Abhimanyu%20Singh%20founded%20%E2%80%98ParkMate%E2%80%99%20to%20tackle%20parking%20challenges%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetter