ed%20to%20try%20to%20lower%20inflation%20and%20boost%20the%20rouble.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67233075%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67233075.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67233075.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22City%20Union%20Bank%20net%20profit%20flat%20at%20Rs%20281%20crore%20in%20September%20quarter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698415814000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F08%2Ffull%2F1696786897-685.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcity-union-bank-net-profit-flat-at-rs-281-crore-in-september-quarter-123102700973_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Interest%20income%20grew%20to%20Rs%201%2C304%20crore%20from%20Rs%201%2C181%20crore%20in%20the%20corresponding%20quarter%20a%20year%20ago%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcity-union-bank-net-profit-flat-at-rs-281-crore-in-september-quarter-123102700973_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcity-union-bank-net-profit-flat-at-rs-281-crore-in-september-quarter-123102700973_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcity-union-bank-net-profit-flat-at-rs-281-crore-in-september-quarter-123102700973_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Coursemate%20Appeals%3A%20Bring%20Back%20Indian%20Navy%20Veterans%20on%20Death%20Row%20in%20Qatar%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27184644%2Fmodi-thani.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sudden%2C%20shocking%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20eight%20former%20Indian%20Navy%20officials%20who%20were%20incarcerated%20in%20Qatar%20on%20unknown%20charges%20since%20August%2030%20last%20year%20were%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37210%2FVerdict_in_the_case_of_8_Indians_detained_in_Qatar%5C%22%3Esentenced%20to%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20by%20a%20Qatari%20%E2%80%98Court%20of%20First%20Instance%E2%80%99.%20Families%20of%20the%20eight%20veterans%20who%20held%20on%20to%20a%20sliver%20of%20hope%20that%20back-channel%20efforts%20may%20secure%20their%20release%20now%20face%20the%20most%20extreme%20prospect%20%E2%80%94%20Death%20Row.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20naval%20veterans%20were%20working%20for%20a%20now-defunct%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fthe-story-behind-qatar-sentencing-eight-indian-ex-navy-officers-to-death%2Farticleshow%2F104731250.cms%5C%22%3EDahra%20Global%20Technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20based%20out%20of%20Doha.%20Their%20area%20of%20expertise%20was%20training%20and%20assisting%20the%20Qatari%20Emiri%20Forces%20in%20setting%20up%20defence%20capacities%20%E2%80%93%20a%20vital%20cog%20in%20the%20wheel%20of%20Indo-Qatar%20bilateral%20defence%20cooperation%20and%20foreign%20policy.%20One%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20countries%20today%2C%20the%20tiny%20kingdom%20of%20Qatar%20has%20traditionally%20enjoyed%20warm%20and%20cordial%20relations%20with%20India.%20Today%2C%20an%20estimated%20diaspora%20of%20800%2C000%20Indians%2C%20along%20with%20other%20nationalities%2C%20contribute%20to%20building%20this%20country%20in%20various%20capacities%2C%20brick%20by%20brick%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Emir%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20Hamad%20Al%20Thani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20the%20present%20case%20are%20far%20too%20sketchy%20and%20opaque%20to%20justify%20such%20an%20extreme%20sentence%20in%20such%20a%20short%20trial.%20There%20have%20hardly%20been%20three%20hearings%20since%20the%20first%20one%20on%20March%2022%20this%20year.%20Since%20their%20incarceration%20in%20August%202022%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20provided%20the%20veterans%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbest%E2%80%9D%20legal%20assistance.%20It%20is%20unlikely%20that%20substantive%20arguments%20from%20the%20(local)%20defence%20counsel%20would%20be%20heard%20and%20addressed%20in%20just%20three%20hearings%20over%20seven%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cdeath%20sentence%E2%80%9D%20has%20left%20the%20Indian%20establishment%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20a%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37210%2FVerdict_in_the_case_of_8_Indians_detained_in_Qatar%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20out%20on%20October%2026%2C%20soon%20after%20sentencing.%20The%20MEA%20statement%20indicates%20an%20%E2%80%98unexpected%20outcome%E2%80%99%20while%20also%20hinting%20at%20the%20opacity%20of%20charges%20framed%20against%20the%20officials.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Qatar%20has%20acted%20in%20complete%20secrecy%2C%20moving%20from%20trial%20to%20conviction%20in%20seven%20months.%20Apparently%2C%20Indian%20authorities%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20complete%20surprise.%20Often%2C%20when%20expectations%20fall%20woefully%20short%20of%20outcome%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20one%20is%20left%20with%20nothing%20but%20tears.%20I%20know%20this%20from%20personal%20experience.%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20affected%20families%2C%20even%20strangers%20with%20a%20conscience%2C%20had%20a%20lump%20in%20their%20throats%20when%20this%20news%20broke%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16130122%2F006_Al_Udeid.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22850%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16130122%2F006_Al_Udeid.jpg%20850w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16130122%2F006_Al_Udeid-300x125.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-644224%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22355%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E006%20Al%20Udeid%2C%20Qatari%20Emiri%20Navy%20Bazan%20class%20off-shore%20patrol%20boat.%20Representative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Murgatroyd49%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20episode%20is%20personal%20at%20many%20levels.%20Two%20of%20the%20eight%20%E2%80%93%20Commander%20Sanjeev%20Gupta%20and%20Commander%20Amit%20Nagpal%20%E2%80%93%20are%20my%20coursemates%2C%20whom%20I%20have%20known%20personally%20for%20over%20four%20decades.%20It%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Efauji%3C%2Fem%3E%20truism%20that%20nobody%20%E2%80%93%20not%20even%20your%20spouse%20%E2%80%93%20knows%20you%20better%20than%20a%20coursemate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESanjeev%20(First%20Course%20of%2010%2B2(X)%2C%20%E2%80%9COceans%20Best%E2%80%9D)%2C%20my%20namesake%20and%20one%20of%20the%20convicted%2C%20was%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Chote%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99%20in%20our%20course.%20His%20small%20frame%20hides%20an%20outsized%20heart%20and%20rock-solid%20patriotism%20while%20his%20ever-helpful%20nature%20earned%20him%20the%20latter%20epithet.%20Such%20is%20his%20obsession%20with%20propriety%20and%20fairness%20that%20on%20one%20of%20my%20earliest%20visits%20to%20his%20hometown%20Agra%2C%20he%20dragged%20my%20errant%20auto%20rickshaw%20driver%20all%20the%20way%20from%20the%20bus%20station%20to%20the%20local%20police%20station%20to%20register%20a%20complaint%20for%20charging%20%E2%80%98excess%20to%20meter%E2%80%99.%20His%20peers%20and%20subordinates%20will%20recount%20numerous%20anecdotes%20where%20his%20%3Cem%3Edildaar%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20can-do%20attitude%20saved%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmit%20(78%20NDA)%20or%20%E2%80%98Naggy%E2%80%99%20as%20we%20call%20him%20in%20our%20circles%2C%20is%20a%20quintessential%20gentleman%20%E2%80%93%20a%20man%20of%20few%20words%20and%20impeccable%20character%20whom%20I%20first%20met%20when%20we%20ran%20into%20our%20NDA%20coursemates%20on%20ships%20of%20the%20training%20squadron%20at%20Kochi.%20A%20communication%20and%20electronic%20warfare%20specialist%2C%20he%20knows%20the%20value%20of%20%E2%80%9Cindiscretion%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cradio%20silence%E2%80%9D%20better%20than%20most.%20Always%20professional%2C%20meticulous%20and%20%E2%80%9Cofficer-like%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20fault%2C%20Naggy%20and%20I%20did%20the%2061st%20staff%20course%20together%20at%20Defence%20Services%20Staff%20College%2C%20Wellington%2C%202005-06.%20I%20cannot%20begin%20to%20fathom%20the%20fate%20that%20befalls%20him%20and%20his%20family%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20can%20sign%20a%20character%20certificate%20for%20these%20two%20officers%20%3Cem%3Ewith%20my%20eyes%20closed%3C%2Fem%3E.%20So%20can%20a%20multitude%20of%20naval%20officials%20who%20have%20known%20or%20worked%20with%20these%20eight%20veterans%2C%20including%20sailor%20Ragesh.%20These%20are%20honest%2C%20above-board%20gentlemen%20who%20worked%20with%20the%20same%20zeal%20and%20commitment%20in%20Indian%20Navy%20service%20as%20in%20their%20selected%20fields%20post-retirement.%20I%20challenge%20those%20who%20know%20them%20personally%20to%20publicly%20reveal%20to%20me%20a%20single%20act%20of%20indiscretion%20that%20even%20remotely%20points%20to%20suspicions%20of%20the%20nature%20they%20have%20allegedly%20been%20charged%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20managing%20director%20of%20their%20enterprise%2C%20Commodore%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%20(I%20do%20not%20know%20him%20personally)%2C%20was%20felicitated%20with%20the%20Pravasi%20Bhartiya%20Samman%20Award%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20at%20a%20glittering%20ceremony%20in%20January%202019%20for%20%E2%80%9Cenhancing%20India%E2%80%99s%20image%20abroad%E2%80%9D.%20Commodore%20Tiwari%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20armed%20forces%20veteran%20to%20be%20awarded%20this%20honour%20meant%20for%20NRIs%2FPIOs.%20How%20did%20these%20character%20certificates%20suddenly%20dissolve%20into%20a%20death%20sentence%3F%20What%20level%20of%20bungling%20led%20to%20this%20impasse%3F%20Whom%20are%20we%20seeking%20to%20protect%3F%20This%20is%20something%20the%20Indian%20government%20needs%20to%20come%20clean%20about.%20Not%20least%20because%20Qatar%20won%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2C%20quite%20obviously%2C%20missing%20pieces%20to%20this%20puzzle%2C%20yet%20to%20be%20uncovered%20by%20investigative%20noses%20from%20India.%20But%2C%20I%20fear%2C%20under%20a%20climate%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eab%20tum%20chup%20raho%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20nosediving%20indices%20of%20press%20freedom%2C%20facts%20may%20never%20come%20out%2C%20even%20if%20they%20lurk%20beneath%20the%20surface%2C%20or%2C%20worse%20still%2C%20point%20to%20the%20establishment.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Qatar%20has%20proceeded%20unapologetically%2C%20thumbing%20their%20noses%20at%20our%20soft-pedalling%20attitude%20(remember%2C%20our%20VP%20visited%20Qatar%20during%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20inaugural).%20The%20latest%20judgment%20can%20best%20be%20described%20as%20a%20resounding%20slap%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Indian%20diplomacy.%20Is%20it%20okay%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D%20at%20such%20travesties%20when%20%3Cem%3EVishwaguru%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20the%20image%20that%20is%20unabashedly%20being%20promoted%20by%20all%20arms%20of%20the%20government%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20fear%20this%20case%20may%20go%20the%20Kulbhushan%20Jadhav%20way%20(another%20very%20unfortunate%20case%2C%20the%20trail%20of%20which%20case%20seems%20to%20have%20gone%20cold)%20unless%20we%20move%20with%20alacrity.%20There%20are%20distinct%20differences%2C%20though%20I%20sincerely%20wish%20India%20had%20done%20more%20for%20Kulbhushan%E2%80%99s%20case.%20Dahra%20Global%20and%20its%20verticals%20were%20doing%20above-ground%20work%20in%20a%20crucial%20area%20of%20Indo-Qatar%20defence%20collaboration.%20This%20space%20would%20undoubtedly%20have%20international%20competitors%20with%20enormous%20clout%2C%20money%20and%20political%20patronage%20who%20would%20(undoubtedly)%20gain%20from%20the%20fall%20of%20Dahra%20Global%20and%20the%20scapegoating%20of%20these%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans.%20Perhaps%20it%20is%20time%20for%20the%20public%2C%20if%20not%20the%20government%2C%20to%20seek%20answers%20to%20the%20old%20police%20maxim%3A%20%E2%80%9CWho%20benefits%20from%20the%20crime%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20terrible%20turn%20of%20events%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20come%20at%20a%20more%20inopportune%20moment%20for%20the%20convicted%20veterans%20and%20their%20families.%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20in%20Qatar%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20going%20concern%2C%20which%20means%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20personnel%20are%20pretty%20much%20on%20their%20own.%20India%E2%80%99s%20nuanced%20position%20on%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20and%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20will%20be%20put%20to%20the%20test%20against%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20emerging%20role%20in%20working%20out%20a%20rapprochement%20between%20the%20Arab%20world%20and%20Israel%2C%20even%20as%20world%20leaders%20weigh%20their%20options.%20Our%20relationship%20with%20Qatar%20will%20head%20south%20if%20the%20ensuing%20diplomatic%20row%20after%20the%20latest%20imbroglio%20is%20not%20settled%20on%20mutually%20acceptable%20terms.%20India%20is%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20fever%2C%20where%20absurd%20theatrics%20and%20sporting%20fervour%20can%20easily%20eclipse%20real-life%20problems.%20If%20all%20this%20is%20not%20bad%20enough%2C%20India%20is%20headed%20into%20a%20general%20election%20season%20where%20parties%20will%20politicise%20every%20available%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%20of%20hypnotising%20billions%20with%20an%20image%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cworld%20leader%E2%80%9D%20or%20Vishwaguru%20is%20that%20sometimes%20problems%20crop%20up%20that%20demand%20the%20full%20agency%20of%20such%20leaders%20to%20step%20in%20and%20solve%20complicated%20problems.%20Now%20the%20unthinkable%20has%20happened%20%E2%80%93%20eight%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans%20are%20on%20death%20row%20in%20a%20friendly%20foreign%20country%20and%20the%20MEA%20under%20our%20strongman%2C%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D.%20Whatever%20that%20means%20in%20diplomacy%2C%20this%20event%20has%20no%20precedence%20in%20modern%20India.%20The%20minions%2C%20influencers%2C%20Ambassadors%20and%20lawyers%20have%20done%20their%20bit%2C%20had%20their%20say.%20No%20more%20passing%20of%20the%20buck%20is%20possible.%20The%20issue%20is%20right%20here%20on%20the%20table%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20ruler%20of%20a%20wealthy%20Middle%20East%20kingdom%20that%20served%20us%2014-month%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBring%20Back%20our%20naval%20veterans%20on%20Death%20Row%20in%20Qatar%20NOW.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKaypius%20is%20the%20pen%20name%20for%20the%20writer%2C%20a%20full-time%20aviator.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20realkaypius%40gmail.com%20and%20tweets%20at%20%40realkaypius.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20the%20writer%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkaypius.com%2F2023%2F10%2F27%2Fa-coursemates-plea-to-bring-back-naval-veterans-on-death-row-in-qatar-now%2F%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698415200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27184644%2Fmodi-thani.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcoursemate-appeal-indian-navy-veterans-death-row-qatar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20downside%20of%20hypnotising%20billions%20with%20an%20image%20of%20%E2%80%9Cworld%20leader%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CVishwaguru%E2%80%9D%20is%20that%20sometimes%20problems%20crop%20up%20that%20demand%20the%20full%20agency%20of%20such%20leaders%20to%20step-in%20and%20solve%20complicated%20problems.%20Now%2C%20the%20unthinkable%20has%20happened.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcoursemate-appeal-indian-navy-veterans-death-row-qatar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20shares%20her%20Whatsapp%20chat%20with%20Shaheen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698415021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104760568%2Cimgsize-31472.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-shares-her-whatsapp-chat-with-sister-shaheen-bhatt-to-give-a-glimpse-of-how-much-she-depends-on-her-sister-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F104760566.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104760566.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAlia%20Bhatt%20gives%20an%20example%20of%20how%20much%20she%20relies%20on%20her%20sister%20Shaheen%20Bhatt%20for%20everything!%20Alia%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%20and%20is%20shooting%20for%20'Jigra'%20which%20she%20has%20also%20co-produced%20with%20Karan%20Johar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-shares-her-whatsapp-chat-with-sister-shaheen-bhatt-to-give-a-glimpse-of-how-much-she-depends-on-her-sister-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F104760566.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Mayawati%E2%80%99s%20Influence%20Wanes%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20Courts%20Dalit%20Community%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172207%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-27-at-4.43.26-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EShamli%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20an%20autumn%20afternoon%20in%20October%2C%20the%20Chamar%20community%20of%20Vikkamajra%20had%20gathered%20to%20listen%20to%20what%20a%20few%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leaders%20had%20to%20say.%20Vikkamajra%20is%20a%20village%20in%20Shamli%20district%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20Chamar%20community%20here%20had%20been%20loyal%20supporters%20of%20the%20Mayawati-led%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20for%20years%2C%20but%20with%20its%20waning%20strength%2C%20is%20now%20open%20to%20weighing%20other%20political%20options.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBehenji%20(Mayawati)%20has%20forgotten%20her%20loyal%20supporters.%20There%20is%20no%20house%20here%20where%20she%20has%20not%20had%20food.%20But%20now%2C%20it%20seems%20she%20has%20deserted%20us.%20Neither%20she%20nor%20her%20leaders%20come%20to%20visit%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyawan%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20community%2C%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResentment%20against%20the%20BSP%20appeared%20to%20be%20widespread.%20For%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20the%20community%20had%20given%20unflinching%20support%20to%20Mayawati%2C%20but%20not%20anymore.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20welcome%20leaders%20of%20other%20parties%20in%20our%20colonies%2C%20but%20unemployment%2C%20back-breaking%20price%20rise%2C%20and%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20reservation%20system%20in%20current%20times%20have%20forced%20us%20to%20listen%20to%20what%20other%20leaders%20have%20to%20say%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyawan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20haven%E2%80%99t%20decided%20anything%20yet.%20But%20we%20are%20weighing%20our%20options.%20The%20party%20best%20placed%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20will%20have%20our%20votes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20Satyawan%2C%20almost%20all%20members%20of%20the%20Chamar%20community%20in%20Vikkamajra%20and%20adjoining%20villages%2C%20were%20highly%20critical%20of%20the%20BJP%20regime.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20such%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emahangai%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(inflation)%20ever%20in%20our%20lives.%20There%20is%20no%20employment%20for%20our%20youth.%20In%20fact%2C%20government%20jobs%20for%20our%20community%20have%20significantly%20decreased%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Salekh%20Chand%20of%20Khatoli%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgorakhpur-ambedkar-jan-morcha-land-rights-crackdown%5C%22%3EIn%20Yogi%E2%80%99s%20Gorakhpur%2C%20an%20Ambedkarite%20Outfit%20Speaking%20for%20Land%20Rights%20Faces%20State%20Crackdown%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%20every%20member%20of%20the%20community%20complained%20about%20the%20poor%20job%20situation%20for%20Dalits%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20the%20reservation%20system%20allowed%20many%20from%20our%20community%20to%20secure%20Group%20C%20and%20D%20jobs%20in%20the%20state%20government.%20Most%20of%20those%20jobs%20are%20now%20outsourced%20to%20private%20entities%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20We%20believe%20that%20such%20outsourcing%20is%20an%20indirect%20way%20to%20end%20the%20reservation%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Salekh%20Chand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20outsourcing%20of%20jobs%20has%20led%20to%20significant%20disillusionment.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20permanent%20jobs%20in%20the%20government%2C%20even%20in%20Groups%20C%20and%20D%2C%20would%20guarantee%20a%20salaried%20income%20of%20around%20Rs%2025%2C000%20per%20month.%20However%2C%20the%20private%20contractors%20give%20us%20only%20around%20Rs%208%2C000%20per%20month.%20How%20do%20you%20expect%20us%20to%20live%20a%20decent%20life%20amidst%20such%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emahangai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Satyawan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERakesh%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20in%20Khatoli%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20schools%20and%20hospitals%20are%20in%20bad%20shape.%20The%20buildings%20look%20quite%20beautiful%20from%20the%20outside%20with%20a%20new%20coat%20of%20paint.%20But%20the%20schools%20do%20not%20have%20enough%20teachers%2C%20the%20hospitals%20do%20not%20have%20enough%20doctors%20or%20para-medical%20staff.%20The%20schools%20are%20there%20only%20to%20serve%20mid-day%20meals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEveryone%20at%20the%20gathering%20also%20complained%20about%20high%20electricity%20bills%20under%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20Akhilesh%20and%20Behenji%20gave%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20welfare%20benefits.%20Our%20electricity%20bills%20were%20considerably%20lower%20during%20their%20tenures.%20But%20with%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20our%20living%20costs%20have%20skyrocketed.%20In%20a%20few%20months%2C%20we%20may%20all%20be%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20starvation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rakesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172158%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-27-at-4.42.26-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172158%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-27-at-4.42.26-PM.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172158%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-27-at-4.42.26-PM-300x183.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682106%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22626%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Chamar%20community%20of%20Khatoli.%20Photo%3A%20Ajoy%20Ashirwad%20Mahaprashasta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20elderly%20man%2C%20Puran%2C%20joined%20in.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20such%20problems%20now.%20But%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20it%20can%20be%20said%20that%20this%20government%20has%20only%20taken%20from%20us%2C%20while%20the%20others%20also%20gave%20something%20in%20return.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20just%20us%20(Chamars)%20but%20also%20communities%20like%20Kashyaps%20(an%20OBC%20community)%20and%20Valmikis%20(another%20Dalit%20community)%2C%20who%20are%20known%20to%20be%20loyal%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20are%20suffering.%20Valmikis%20have%20stopped%20getting%20permanent%20safai%20karamachari%20jobs%2C%20while%20Kashyaps%20who%20run%20Kolhus%20(small-scale%20jaggery%20making%20units)%20in%20the%20region%20are%20reeling%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20high%20electricity%20bills%2C%E2%80%9D%20Puran%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20Chamar%20community%20will%20vote%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20appears%20to%20be%20clear.%20But%20which%20way%20will%20they%20swing%20seems%20to%20be%20undecided%2C%20as%20the%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20is%20clearly%20dwindling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opportunity%20has%20seen%20parties%20like%20the%20SP%2C%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20Dalits%20of%20Shamli.%20SP%20is%20the%20first%20to%20address%20the%20concerns%20of%20Chamars%20living%20in%20Vikkamajra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20leaders%20who%20addressed%20the%20meeting%20was%20Sudhir%20Panwar%2C%20a%20Lucknow%20University%20professor%20and%20SP%20leader%20belonging%20to%20the%20Jat%20community.%20Panwar%20had%20unsuccessfully%20contested%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls%20from%20the%20Thana%20Bhawan%20constituency%20in%202017%20and%20has%20since%20then%20been%20active%20in%20expanding%20the%20SP%20voter%20base%20among%20Dalits%20in%20the%20locality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20haven%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20seek%20votes.%20The%202024%20elections%20are%20still%20six%20months%20away.%20We%20have%20come%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20our%20leader%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20given%20the%20call%20to%20unite%20%3Cem%3Epichda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dalit%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ealpasankhayak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(PDA%20or%20OBC%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Bahujan%20communities)%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20Dalits%20will%20have%20a%20proportionate%20share%20of%20power%20in%20our%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20Panwar%20told%20the%20gathering%2C%20as%20he%20also%20let%20the%20audience%20speak%20about%20their%20doubts%20and%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPanwar%20echoed%20the%20Dalit%20sentiment%20that%20Mayawati%20has%20largely%20been%20inactive%20in%20taking%20up%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20poor.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20her%20silence%20on%20critical%20issues%20means%20only%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%93%20that%20she%20is%20indirectly%20supporting%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Panwar%20says%2C%20as%20he%20goes%20on%20to%20name%20a%20string%20of%20former%20ground-level%20BSP%20leaders%20in%20the%20region%20who%20have%20now%20joined%20the%20SP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPanwar%20believes%20that%20the%20SP%20is%20the%20only%20relatable%20option%20for%20the%20Dalits%20if%20they%20choose%20to%20move%20away%20from%20the%20BSP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20agrarian%20crisis%20over%20the%20last%20few%20decades%20has%20impoverished%20the%20agrarian%20OBC%20castes%20like%20Jats%2C%20Yadavs%20and%20others.%20A%20majority%20of%20Dalits%20in%20the%20region%20prefer%20private%20jobs%20over%20agricultural%20labour%20work.%20However%2C%20even%20there%2C%20wage%20rates%20have%20stagnated%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%20Outsourcing%20of%20Group%20C%20and%20D%20government%20jobs%20has%20made%20them%20poorer.%20The%20traditional%20conflict%20between%20the%20OBC%20and%20Dalits%20at%20the%20village%20level%20has%20diminished%20greatly%20now.%20In%20such%20circumstances%2C%20the%20SP%20can%20be%20the%20only%20party%20that%20can%20take%20up%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20poor%2C%E2%80%9D%20Panwar%20says%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emaalik-naukar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(owner-servant)%20relationship%20between%20agrarian%20castes%20and%20Dalits%20has%20become%20almost%20non-existent.%20Because%20of%20that%20conflictual%20relationship%2C%20Dalits%20never%20voted%20for%20parties%20led%20by%20agrarian%20castes%20like%20Yadavs%20or%20Jats.%20Initially%2C%20Dalits%20voted%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20then%20switched%20to%20the%20BSP%2C%20while%20agrarian%20castes%20consolidated%20behind%20leaders%20like%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20and%20Charan%20Singh%2C%E2%80%9D%20Panwar%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172145%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-27-at-4.40.13-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172145%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-27-at-4.40.13-PM.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172145%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-27-at-4.40.13-PM-300x183.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682105%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22626%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESP%20leader%20Sudhir%20Panwar%20addresses%20a%20small%20Dalit%20gathering%20in%20Vikkamajra.%20Photo%3A%20Ajoy%20Ashirwad%20Mahaprashasta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20some%20Dalit%20groups%20also%20experimented%20with%20the%20BJP%20as%20the%20BSP%20began%20to%20decline%20but%2C%20according%20to%20Panwar%2C%20have%20begun%20to%20realise%20that%20non-Brahminical%20parties%20like%20the%20SP%20are%20their%20best%20bet%20in%20the%20longer%20run.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20collapse%20of%20the%20BSP%20in%20recent%20times%20means%20that%20Dalits%20are%20losing%20their%20voters%E2%80%99%20contract%20with%20a%20mainstream%20political%20party.%20That%20has%20led%20to%20a%20significant%20churn%20among%20Dalit%20communities.%20We%20in%20the%20SP%2C%20therefore%2C%20are%20earnestly%20trying%20to%20bring%20them%20into%20our%20fold%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Panwar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20SP%E2%80%99s%20Dalit%20outreach%20has%20systematically%20increased%20in%20recent%20times.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20surrounded%20himself%20with%20Dalit%20and%20non-Yadav%20OBC%20leaders%20on%20almost%20every%20platform.%20His%20chief%20aides%20are%20considered%20to%20be%20Awadhesh%20Prasad%2C%20a%20Pasi%20Dalit%20leader%2C%20Ram%20Achal%20Rajbhar%2C%20an%20OBC%20Rajbhar%20leader%2C%20and%20Lalji%20Verma%2C%20a%20Khushwaha%20OBC%20leader.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20also%20formed%20a%20Dalit%20outreach%20organisation%20called%20Ambedkar%20Vahini%20and%20entrusted%20its%20functioning%20to%20former%20BSP%20leaders%20who%20still%20have%20their%20ground-level%20connections%20intact.%20Speaking%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Ambedkar%20Vahini%20president%20and%20former%20BSP%20leader%20Mithai%20Lal%20Bharati%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20joined%20the%20SP%20as%20we%20felt%20the%20BSP%20had%20slowed%20down%20the%20Dalit%20movement%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20There%20was%20no%20space%20for%20critical%20feedback%20in%20the%20party.%20Yet%2C%20we%20felt%20happy%20when%20the%20BSP%20and%20SP%20came%20together%20in%202019.%20But%20then%20Behenji%20unilaterally%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Futtar-pradesh-sp-bsp-alliance-bjp%5C%22%3Ebreak%20the%20alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20any%20discussion%20with%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20district%20presidents%20like%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20realised%20that%20the%20BSP%20could%20win%20some%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20only%20because%20of%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP.%20But%20she%20was%20ungrateful.%20She%20took%20leaders%20like%20us%20for%20granted.%20Both%20BSP%20and%20SP%20leaders%20could%20not%20stand%20each%20other%20after%20the%201995%20guest%20house%20incident.%20But%20it%20was%20Behenji%20who%20bridged%20that%20gap%20by%20allying%20with%20Akhileshji.%20Then%20she%20broke%20the%20relationship%20again%2C%20once%20the%20workers%20of%20both%20parties%20had%20become%20friendly%20to%20each%20other.%20She%20should%20not%20have%20broken%20that%20alliance%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bharati%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20so%20much%20provocation%20by%20Behenji%2C%20Akhileshji%20didn%E2%80%99t%20utter%20a%20single%20word%20against%20her.%20Even%20the%20SP%20workers%20are%20welcoming%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172807%2Fmayawati-akhilesh.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172807%2Fmayawati-akhilesh.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172807%2Fmayawati-akhilesh-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172807%2Fmayawati-akhilesh-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172807%2Fmayawati-akhilesh-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682114%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMayawati%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%20Photos%3A%20X%2F%40Mayawati%2C%20%40samajwadiparty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharati%20said%20his%20goal%20was%20to%20form%20Ambedkar%20Vahini%20committees%20at%20every%20booth%20of%20UP%20until%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20begun%20to%20see%20some%20positive%20results.%20The%20bypolls%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fbypoll-results-live-updates-september-2023-ghosi-bageshwar-puthuppally-dhupguri-dumri-boxanagar-dhanpur-101694133746179.html%5C%22%3EGhosi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fkhatauli-bypoll-election-results-2022-updates-rld-madan-bhaiya-bjp-rajkumari-saini%2Farticleshow%2F96079888.cms%5C%22%3EKhatauli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Mirzapur%20Chhanbey%20saw%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20Dalits%20voting%20for%20the%20SP%20or%20its%20allies.%20We%20plan%20to%20capitalise%20on%20that.%20The%20SP%20is%20the%20natural%20option%20for%20Dalits%20after%20the%20BSP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharati%20believes%20that%20if%20the%20SP%20drives%20home%20the%20PDA%20message%20effectively%2C%20even%20those%20Dalit%20groups%20who%20have%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20last%20two%20elections%20will%20change%20their%20minds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDalits%20have%20realised%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20a%20party%20that%20prefers%20the%20rich%20over%20the%20poor.%20The%20tokenisms%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20enough%20anymore.%20Congress%20is%20non-existent%20in%20UP.%20The%20SP%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20a%20natural%20social%20justice%20party%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20number%20of%20former%20BSP%20ground-level%20leaders%20have%20joined%20the%20SP%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20However%2C%20the%20SP%20leaders%20agree%20that%20only%20if%20the%20party%20is%20able%20to%20entice%20top-level%20BSP%20leaders%20can%20it%20truly%20tap%20into%20the%20political%20churn%20among%20Dalits%20and%20emerge%20as%20a%20force%20to%20reckon%20with.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%20SP%20appears%20to%20be%20clear%20that%20only%20by%20securing%20the%20confidence%20of%20Dalits%2C%20it%20can%20expand%20its%20vote%20share%20beyond%20the%20traditional%20voter%20base%20of%20OBC%20and%20Muslims.%20Dalits%20represent%20the%20most%20crucial%20element%20of%20the%20PDA%20formula%20that%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20speaks%20about.%20They%20remain%20the%20only%20factor%20that%20could%20elevate%20the%20party%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20formidable%20BJP%2C%20which%20secured%20around%2050%25%20of%20the%20total%20votes%20polled%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698413440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27172207%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-27-at-4.43.26-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmayawati-influence-wanes-samajwadi-party-court-dalit-community%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20Dalit%20communities%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20facing%20the%20brunt%20of%20high%20inflation%20and%20unemployment.%20With%20many%20of%20them%20disenchanted%20with%20the%20BSP%2C%20other%20opposition%20parties%20are%20attempting%20to%20make%20inroads.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmayawati-influence-wanes-samajwadi-party-court-dalit-community%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vir%20Das%20advocates%20for%20Deepika%20Padukone.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698413281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104759712%2Cimgsize-29524.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%