%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20V.P.%20Menon%20Viewed%20the%20Future%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3A%20A%20Vignette%20From%20October%201947%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27160736%2Fvp-menon.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20V.K.%20Saxena%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-lg-grants-sanction-prosecute-arundhati-roy-2010-case%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egreen-signalled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20prosecute%20Arundhati%20Roy%20and%20professor%20Sheikh%20Showkat%20Hussain%20for%20speaking%20their%20minds%20about%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(J%26amp%3BK)%20at%20a%20public%20event%2013%20years%20ago.%20The%20former%20is%20a%20Booker%20Prize-winning%20author%20and%20public%20intellectual%20who%20does%20not%20hesitate%20to%20call%20a%20spade%2C%20be%20it%20matters%20relating%20to%20society%2C%20polity%2C%20economy%20or%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20entire%20planet.%20She%20preferred%20to%20spend%20a%20full%20day%20in%20prison%20rather%20than%20tender%20an%20apology%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20for%20expressing%20views%20that%20the%20court%20deemed%20contemptuous%20of%20its%20majesty.%20The%20latter%20is%20a%20noted%20academic%20who%20trained%20generations%20of%20students%20in%20law%20and%20human%20rights%20but%20was%20unceremoniously%20removed%20as%20the%20principal%20of%20Kashmir%20Law%20College%20last%20year%20for%20views%20he%20publicly%20expressed%20about%20J%26amp%3BK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20will%20stand%20trial%20for%20the%20alleged%20offences%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epromoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20and%20residence%2C%20and%20for%20allegedly%20making%20imputations%2C%20and%20assertions%20prejudicial%20to%20national%20integration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Two%20other%20co-accused%20have%20passed%20away%20during%20the%20pendency%20of%20these%20proceedings.%20However%2C%20the%20charge%20of%20%E2%80%98sedition%E2%80%99%20that%20was%20hurled%20at%20all%20of%20them%20by%20the%20complainant%20%E2%80%93%20a%20J%26amp%3BK-based%20activist%20%E2%80%93%20will%20not%20be%20tried%20due%20to%20a%20Supreme%20Court-imposed%20stay%20on%20all%20proceedings%20relating%20to%20that%20offence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMedia%20reports%20indicate%20that%20the%20complainant%20approached%20the%20Delhi%20police%20because%20he%20found%20their%20speech%20provocative%20and%20supportive%20of%20the%20aspirations%20for%20%E2%80%98freedom%E2%80%99%20that%20were%20being%20aired%20at%20that%20time%20by%20some%20individuals%20and%20groups%20in%20relation%20to%20J%26amp%3BK.%20None%20of%20the%20case-related%20papers%2C%20including%20the%20sanction%20accorded%20for%20their%20prosecution%2C%20are%20publicly%20available.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20court%20finds%20in%20the%20evidence%20presented%20before%20it%20any%20ingredients%20of%20the%20offences%20of%20which%20these%20two%20public-spirited%20citizens%20stand%20accused.%20The%20experience%20in%20recent%20years%20indicates%20that%20any%20person%20commenting%20about%20these%20matters%2C%20let%20alone%20supporting%20them%2C%20becomes%20the%20immediate%20target%20of%20troll%20mobs%20on%20social%20media%20and%20jingoistic%20anchors%20on%20electronic%20media%20platforms%20and%20is%20labelled%20an%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20what%20do%20we%20make%20of%20the%20views%20of%20the%20gentleman%20who%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20process%20of%20securing%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20integration%20with%20India%20in%201947%20and%20also%20favoured%20freedom%20for%20that%20part%20of%20the%20sub-continent%20in%20the%20long%20run%3F%20On%20the%2076%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20anniversary%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20accession%20to%20India%2C%20this%20little-known%20vignette%20from%20that%20turbulent%20phase%20of%20modern%20Indian%20history%20is%20being%20presented%20with%20the%20fond%20hope%20that%20issues%20like%20%E2%80%9Cfreedom%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cself-determination%E2%80%9D%20are%20debated%20with%20a%20lot%20more%20care%20and%20maturity.%20The%20aspiration%20to%20be%20recognised%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmother%20of%20democracies%E2%80%9D%20must%20be%20accompanied%20by%20credible%20efforts%20to%20recognise%20and%20understand%2C%20not%20stifle%20and%20penalise%2C%20the%20expression%20of%20divergent%20views%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReaders%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20crucial%20role%20which%20Vappala%20Pangunni%20Menon%20(V.P.%20Menon)%20played%20in%20bringing%20together%20the%20500-odd%20princely%20states%2C%20zamindaris%20and%20the%20provinces%20directly%20administered%20by%20the%20British%20Raj%20to%20form%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20between%201947%20and%201949.%20Initially%20as%20secretary%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20States%20and%20later%20as%20its%20Special%20Advisor%2C%20he%20achieved%20this%20formidable%20task%20under%20the%20leadership%20and%20guidance%20of%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%2C%20the%20Iron%20Man%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20seminal%20work%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Story%20of%20the%20Integration%20of%20Indian%20States%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Menon%20narrates%20the%20circumstances%20which%20led%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20acceding%20to%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20While%20recounting%20the%20bare%20facts%20about%20the%20flurry%20of%20meetings%20in%20Delhi%20and%20his%20own%20hurried%20travels%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%20October%201947%20to%20secure%20its%20accession%2C%20he%20intentionally%20abstains%20from%20sharing%20his%20own%20views%20about%20these%20matters%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20the%20narration%20of%20facts%20as%20objective%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20However%2C%20his%20personal%20views%20about%20J%26amp%3BK%20have%20been%20documented%20for%20posterity%20in%20the%20official%20record%20of%20the%20deliberations%20of%20the%20Defence%20Committee%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%201947.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20public%20knowledge%20that%20Menon%20flew%20to%20Srinagar%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOctober%2025%2C%201947%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20this%20Committee.%20Its%208%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20meeting%20held%20earlier%20that%20day%20was%20chaired%20by%20governor%20general%20Lord%20Mountbatten%2C%20and%20attended%20by%20prime%20minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20defence%20minister%20Sardar%20Baldev%20Singh%2C%20finance%20minister%20R.K.%20Shanmukham%20Chetty%20and%20the%20minister-without-portfolio%20N.%20Gopalaswamy%20Ayyangar.%20The%20heads%20of%20the%20three%20defence%20forces%2C%20and%20a%20host%20of%20secretaries%20and%20advisors%20representing%20key%20ministries%20were%20also%20present.%20The%20previous%20day%2C%20the%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20of%20the%20princely%20state%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20R.L.%20Batra%2C%20had%20arrived%20in%20Delhi%20with%20an%20SOS%20message%20from%20Maharaja%20Hari%20Singh%20as%20hordes%20of%20tribes%20were%20pouring%20in%20from%20across%20the%20northwestern%20border%2C%20committing%20murder%2C%20rape%2C%20arson%20and%20looting%20in%20village%20after%20village%20and%20town%20after%20town.%20They%20were%20less%20than%2050%20miles%20away%20from%20Srinagar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMenon%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20was%20to%20discuss%20with%20Maharaja%20Hari%20Singh%2C%20among%20other%20things%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20possibilities%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20requesting%20armed%20assistance%20from%20India%20to%20defend%20the%20territory%20from%20the%20marauding%20infiltrators%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Ecooperation%20between%20the%20government%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20the%20National%20Conference%20led%20by%20Shaikh%20Mohammed%20Abdullah%3B%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EJ%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20willingness%20to%20accede%20to%20the%20Dominion%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMenon%20flew%20back%20to%20Delhi%20on%20October%2026%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20meeting%20the%20maharaja%20in%20Srinagar%20and%20advising%20him%20to%20move%20to%20Jammu%20with%20his%20family%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20their%20safety.%20He%20reported%20his%20observations%20to%20the%20Defence%20Committee%20at%20its%209%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20meeting%20held%20the%20same%20day.%20The%20Committee%20advised%20him%20to%20fly%20back%20to%20Kashmir%20to%20secure%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20accession%20to%20India.%20The%20exact%20date%20and%20time%20of%20his%20next%20round%20of%20travel%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20have%20become%20a%20matter%20of%20controversy%20thanks%20to%20the%20varying%20narratives%20published%20by%20Indian%20and%20foreign%20historians%20and%20authors.%20I%20hope%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20issue%20later%20this%20year%2C%20based%20on%20archival%20research.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fpublic-first-time-jammu-kashmirs-instrument-accession-india%5C%22%3EThe%20Backstory%20of%20Article%20370%3A%20A%20True%20Copy%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Instrument%20of%20Accession%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20publicly%20available%20official%20records%20and%20narratives%20are%20unanimous%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20Lord%20Mountbatten%20accepted%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Instrument%20of%20Accession%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20October%2027%2C%201947%20when%20it%20was%20presented%20to%20him%20with%20the%20signature%20of%20Maharaja%20Hari%20Singh.%20Its%20text%20and%20the%20maharaja%E2%80%99s%20letter%20explaining%20the%20dire%20situation%20that%20had%20arisen%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20were%20published%20in%20the%20pages%20of%20local%20and%20foreign%20media%20on%20October%2028%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20is%20in%20the%20record%20of%20the%20Defence%20Committee%E2%80%99s%2010%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20meeting%20held%20on%20that%20day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0that%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20personal%20and%20unequivocal%20opinion%20about%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20future%20can%20be%20found.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20chain%20of%20the%20conversation%20is%20summarised%20briefly%20below.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F680470568%2FMinutes-of-the-10th-meeting-of-the-Defence-Committee-held-on-October-28-1947%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Minutes%20of%20the%2010th%20meeting%20of%20the%20Defence%20Committee%20held%20on%20October%2028%2C%201947%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EMinutes%20of%20the%2010th%20meeting%20of%20the%20Defence%20Committee%20held%20on%20October%2028%2C%201947%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F286754081%2FThe-Wire%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20The%20Wire's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F680470568%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-7pQS9c0oHQLg5IgXln6K%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7068965517241379%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Minutes%20of%20the%2010th%20meeting%20of%20the%20Defence%20Committee%20held%20on%20October%2028%2C%201947%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Defence%20Committee%20discussed%20at%20length%20the%20progress%20made%20by%20the%20Indian%20defence%20forces%20which%20had%20landed%20in%20Srinagar%20the%20previous%20morning.%20Then%20the%20deliberations%20moved%20on%20to%20comparing%20the%20situation%20in%20Junagadh%2C%20Gujarat%20whose%20ruler%20professing%20the%20Islamic%20faith%20was%20inclined%20to%20accede%20to%20the%20Dominion%20of%20Pakistan%20whereas%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20population%20were%20Hindus.%20In%20contrast%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20had%20a%20very%20large%20population%20of%20Muslims%20but%20was%20ruled%20by%20a%20Hindu%20Maharaja.%20Lord%20Mountbatten%20was%20of%20the%20view%20that%20India%20was%20in%20a%20strong%20position%20because%20it%20had%20declared%20its%20intention%20of%20ascertaining%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%20in%20Kashmir%20on%20final%20accession%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20there%20allowed%20it.%20So%2C%20it%20would%20automatically%20follow%20that%20Pakistan%20would%20accept%20a%20similar%20procedure%20for%20Junagadh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Nehru%20opined%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20states%20as%20a%20whole%20would%20improve%20enormously%20if%20things%20went%20well%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20would%20be%20correspondingly%20weakened%20if%20there%20was%20excessive%20delay%20in%20clearing%20up%20Kashmir%20and%20if%20India%20became%20entangled%20there%20for%20a%20long%20period.%20Sardar%20Patel%20said%20that%20as%20far%20as%20world%20opinion%20was%20concerned%2C%20the%20longer%20the%20Junagadh%20situation%20was%20prolonged%2C%20the%20bigger%20an%20issue%20and%20more%20insoluble%20it%20would%20become.%20Shanmugam%20Chetty%20pointed%20out%20that%20world%20opinion%20usually%20ends%20up%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20victorious%20party%20in%20any%20clash.%20He%20said%20that%20military%20preparations%20should%20be%20made%20in%20Kashmir%20for%20any%20hostile%20action%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGopalaswami%20Ayyangar%20remarked%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20case%20in%20both%20Kashmir%20and%20Junagadh%20was%20very%20strong%20from%20a%20political%20point%20of%20view.%20General%20William%20Lockhart%2C%20the%20then%20commander-in-chief%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20said%20he%20saw%20Kashmir%20developing%20into%20a%20very%20big%20commitment%20indeed.%20He%20also%20said%20it%20was%20doubtful%20whether%20it%20would%20be%20in%20the%20power%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20to%20restore%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20whole%20of%20Kashmir%20if%20it%20became%20a%20question%20of%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Nehru%20added%20that%20the%20task%20of%20eventually%20clearing%20Poonch%20was%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20terrific%20job%20%5Bsic%5D%20and%20that%20it%20could%20probably%20not%20be%20taken%20up%20at%20all%20until%20the%20winter%20was%20over.%20Lord%20Mountbatten%20pointed%20out%20that%20British%20officers%20would%20not%20be%20available%20to%20help%20in%20a%20plebiscite%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20following%20spring.%20He%20advised%20that%20the%20UN%20or%20the%20UK%20government%20be%20asked%20to%20send%20out%20officials%20to%20help%20with%20the%20plebiscite%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20Junagadh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20point%20at%20which%20the%20minutes%20of%20the%20Defence%20Committee%20meeting%20record%20V.P.%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20what%20he%20expects%20to%20be%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20best-case%20scenario%20for%20the%20future%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMr.%20Menon%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20two%20were%20not%20identical%20problems.%20Junagadh%20was%20a%20comparatively%20straight%20issue%20whereas%20Kashmir%20had%20relations%20with%20both%20Dominions%20and%20frontiers%20with%20other%20countries.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20best%20solution%20in%20the%20end%20might%20be%20for%20Kashmir%20to%20remain%20independent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20%5BEmphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27161640%2FImage-07.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22850%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27161640%2FImage-07.jpg%20850w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27161640%2FImage-07-213x300.jpg%20213w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27161640%2FImage-07-725x1024.jpg%20725w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682092%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPage%205%20of%20the%20Minutes%20of%20the%2010th%20Defence%20Committee%20meeting%20held%20on%20October%2028%2C%201947.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENothing%20in%20the%20minutes%20show%20either%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20under%20whose%20guidance%20and%20instructions%20Menon%20worked%2C%20or%20Prime%20Minister%20Nehru%20or%20Lord%20Mountbatten%20or%20other%20participants%20rebuking%20him%20for%20talking%20about%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20independence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20ink%20on%20the%20Instrument%20of%20Accession%20signed%20and%20accepted%20less%20than%2048%20hours%20ago%20had%20barely%20dried%20when%20Menon%20spoke%20his%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20why%20is%20this%20vignette%20of%20history%20important%20in%202023%3F%20Had%20Menon%20been%20alive%20today%20and%20uttered%20these%20views%2C%20would%20he%20not%20be%20accused%20of%20supporting%20%E2%80%98separatism%E2%80%99%3F%20Would%20his%20patriotism%20and%20commitment%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20not%20be%20thrust%20under%20a%20public%20scanner%20ignoring%20his%20yeoman%20contribution%20to%20unify%20India%20territorially%20and%20administratively%3F%20Would%20he%20not%20be%20trolled%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etukde%20tukde%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20gang%E2%80%99%20on%20social%20media%3F%20Would%20he%20not%20be%20hauled%20up%20for%20%E2%80%98sedition%E2%80%99%20and%20for%20%E2%80%98making%20assertions%20against%20national%20integration%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20manner%20of%20Arundhati%20Roy%20and%20Sheikh%20Showkat%20Hussain%3F%20Or%20will%20the%20foot%20soldiers%20of%20a%20certain%20ideological%20disposition%20now%20conduct%20a%20media%20trial%20of%20V.P.%20Menon%20posthumously%20and%20move%20him%20from%20the%20ranks%20of%20%E2%80%98patriots%E2%80%99%20to%20those%20of%20%E2%80%98anti-nationals%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20vignette%20of%20history%20serves%20as%20testimony%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20that%20existed%20in%20independent%20India%20even%20when%20the%20constitution%20had%20not%20been%20put%20in%20place%20to%20protect%20it.%20There%20was%20space%20within%20the%20highest%20government%20circles%20for%20voicing%20divergent%20views%20without%20fear%20of%20reprisals.%20Do%20similar%20spaces%20for%20the%20expression%20of%20contrarian%20views%20exist%20within%20and%20outside%20government%20circles%20today%2C%20in%20the%20era%20of%20nasty%20trolling%20and%20fake%20news%20peddling%3F%20This%20is%20what%20every%20citizen%20must%20be%20deeply%20worried%20about.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20the%20biggest%20irony%20of%20the%20Roy-Hussain%20episode%20is%20that%20the%20gentleman%20who%20accorded%20sanction%20for%20their%20prosecution%20himself%20stands%20accused%20of%20committing%20serious%20offences%20such%20as%20assault%2C%20wrongful%20restraint%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%20and%20being%20part%20of%20an%20unlawful%20assembly%2C%20along%20with%20three%20other%20politicians%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2F2002-assault-case-gujarat-hc-to-hear-delhi-lieutenant-governor-vk-saxenas-plea-on-june-30%2Farticleshow%2F101185803.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ecase%20that%20is%20more%20than%2021%20years%20old%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Noted%20environmental%20activist%20and%20advocate%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20people%20displaced%20by%20developmental%20projects%2C%20Medha%20Patkar%20of%20the%20Narmada%20Bachao%20Andolan%2C%20was%20allegedly%20assaulted%20by%20this%20quartet%20at%2C%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20Sabarmati%20Ashram%20in%202002.%20While%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20criminal%20trial%20on%20his%20plea%20that%20he%20is%20required%20to%20perform%20his%20constitutional%20duties%20as%20the%20Delhi%20LG%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20granted%20his%20plea%20earlier%20this%20year.%20In%20an%20ideal%20world%2C%20such%20a%20person%20ought%20to%20have%20voluntarily%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20constitutional%20office%20to%20face%20trial%20instead%20of%20moving%20high%20court%20after%20high%20court%20for%20relief.%20But%20we%20are%20told%2C%20we%20are%20living%20in%20Amrit%20Kaal.%2C%20not%20ideal%20times%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fvenkatesh-nayak%5C%22%3EVenkatesh%20Nayak%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20RTI%20activist%20and%20a%20history%20researcher%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698409845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27160736%2Fvp-menon.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fvp-jammu-and-kashmir-future-freedom-of-expression%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sa