%5C%22%3Estated%20bluntly%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Palestinian%20people%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%2056%20years%20of%20suffocating%20occupation%E2%80%A6%20But%20the%20grievances%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20cannot%20justify%20the%20appalling%20attacks%20by%20Hamas.%20And%20those%20appalling%20attacks%20cannot%20justify%20the%20collective%20punishment%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20intolerable%20for%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20governed%20as%20it%20is%20by%20the%20most%20extreme%20government%20it%20has%20ever%20had%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20quickly%20called%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F10%2F25%2Fantonio-guterres-israel-envoy-calls-for-un-chiefs-resignation.html%5C%22%3EGuterres%20to%20resign%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Strikingly%2C%20not%20one%20other%20country%2C%20not%20even%20the%20United%20States%2C%20sided%20with%20Israel.%20In%20fact%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20renewed%20his%20call%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2Fbiden-post-war-plan-two-state-solution-israel-palestinians%5C%22%3Ea%20Two%20State%20solution%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20something%20he%20has%20largely%20avoided%20addressing%20during%20his%20presidency.%20Given%20how%20often%20the%20US%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Arab%20dictatorships%20have%20paid%20only%20lip%20service%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20Palestinian%20statehood%2C%20Israel%20may%20feel%20that%20this%20too%2C%20will%20pass.%20This%20would%20be%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchart-6407-palestinians-and-308-israelis-killed-in-violence-in-last-15-years%5C%22%3EChart%3A%206%2C407%20Palestinians%20and%20308%20Israelis%20Killed%20in%20Violence%20in%20Last%2015%20Years%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20many%20deaths%20does%20it%20take%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20war%20grinds%20on%2C%20and%20casualti