hasises%2C%20the%20job%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20set%20of%20demands.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20work%20in%20a%20hostile%20environment%20wearing%20gear%2C%20helmet%2C%20bulletproof%20jackets%2C%20etc%2C%20all%20while%20trying%20to%20click%20the%20perfect%20picture%20while%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20the%20action%2C%20and%20ensuring%20you%20are%20not%20obstructing%20someone%E2%80%99s%20duty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20real%20challenge%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20taking%20advantage%20of%20every%20moment.%20%E2%80%9CA%20missile%20is%20only%20fired%20once%20and%20you%20have%20a%20moment%20to%20get%20your%20shot.%20That%20moment%20won%E2%80%99t%20come%20back.%20Every%20instance%2C%20every%20picture%20has%20its%20own%20glory.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Vidyasagar%20Hariharan%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201066px)%20100vw%2C%201066px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20complex%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai.%20Image%20credit%3A%20Vidyasagar%20Hariharan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202.jpeg%201066w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202-768x1153.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202-1023x1536.jpeg%201023w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202-150x225.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C