0en%20route.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20noon%20when%20it%20was%20time%20to%20leave%2C%20the%20participants%20would%20be%20treated%20to%20a%20special%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eprasadam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20prepared%20in%20the%20house.%20Savitri%2C%20who%20has%20been%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20help%20for%2035%20years%2C%20also%20helped%20in%20the%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESrimathi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20teachers%2C%20recollects%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20uncle%20(Mr%20Iyengar)%20pitching%20in%20some%20times%20to%20prepare%20some%20special%20food%20like%20Pizza.%20He%20would%20make%20it%20from%20scratch.%20Once%20he%20was%20preparing%20%3Cem%3Ealoo%20bonda%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20I%20was%20helping%20him%20roll%20the%20potatoes.%20I%20remember%20him%20telling%20me%20to%20make%20them%20big%20enough%20so%20that%20the%20kids%20could%20have%20their%20fill.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20initially%20they%20would%20collect%20Rs%2025%20from%20each%20student%2C%20in%20later%20years%20the%20amount%20was%20increased%20to%20Rs%201000.%20This%20was%20used%20for%20materials%20required%20for%20the%20classes.%20%E2%80%9CAnything%20remaining%20after%20the%20camp%20would%20be%20donated%20to%20NGOs%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mamatha.%20On%20Sundays%2C%20they%20would%20plan%20some%20special%20activity%2C%20like%20going%20on%20an%20excursion%20to%20nearby%20places%20or%20a%20bird-watching%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20camps%20that%20usually%20ran%20for%203-4%20weeks%20were%20based%20on%20a%20theme%20every%20year.%20This%20would%20be%20decided%20mostly%20by%20Sudha%20but%20in%20consultation%20with%20her%20team%20of%20teachers.%20%E2%80%9CInnovative%20ideas%20were%20welcomed%2C%20like%20the%20%3Cem%3EAata%20Oota%3C%2Fem%3E%20Camp%2C%20which%20involved%20making%20food%20without%20cooking.%20Also%2C%20each%20team%20would%20be%20named%20by%20a%20food%20item%20they%20did%20not%20like.%20This%20was%20done%20to%20foster%20a%20change%20of%20attitude%20towards%20the%20food%20item.%20After%20all%2C%20you%20cannot%20not%20like%20your%20team!%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Srimathi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20come%20to%20enrol%20her%20son%20for%20the%20camp%20but%20felt%20drawn%20to%20assist%20a%20child%20with%20disabilities%20in%20the%20camp.%20Observing%20her%20patience%20and%20how%20the%20child%20obeyed%20her%2C%20Sudha%20took%20it%20upon%20herself%20to%20talk%20to%20Srimathi%E2%80%99s%20husband.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20asked%20him%20to%20get%20me%20admitted%20into%20some%20course%20and%20not%20let%20my%20talent%20go%20to%20waste.%20I%20went%20on%20to%20do%20a%20Montessori%20course%20and%20now%20I%20run%20my%20own%20school.%20I%20have%20her%20picture%20alongside%20that%20of%20God%20in%20my%20house%20and%20I%20bow%20to%20both.%20She%20is%20my%20living%20God%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20explaining%20how%20this%20turned%20her%20life%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20an%20exhibition%20would%20be%20organised%20for%20the%20parents%20where%20they%20could%20see%20what%20their%20children%20had%20been%20doing%20during%20the%20camp.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332881%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20an%20exhibition%20would%20be%20organised%20for%20the%20parents%20where%20they%20could%20see%20what%20their%20children%20had%20been%20doing%20during%20the%20camp.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20practical%20knowledge%20was%20imparted%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EChildren%20of%20the%20camp%20were%20taught%20basic%20transactional%20skills%20like%20handling%20money%2C%20attending%20to%20customers%2C%20convincing%20skills%2C%20among%20others.%20For%20this%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98sante%E2%80%99%20was%20held%20where%20they%20would%20sell%20some%20items%20like%20craft%2C%20food%2C%20games%20and%20greeting%20cards%20to%20parents%2C%20teachers%20and%20friends%20who%20dropped%20in.%20The%20parents%2C%20mostly%20mothers%2C%20and%20grandparents%20used%20to%20pitch%20in%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20an%20exhibition%20would%20be%20organised%20for%20the%20parents%20where%20they%20could%20see%20what%20their%20children%20had%20been%20doing%20during%20the%20camp.%20A%20two-hour%20performance%20by%20the%20students%20would%20be%20followed%20with%20tea%20and%20snacks%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20an%20MS%20patient%20manage%20to%20do%20all%20this%3F%20Ask%20her%20and%20Sudha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20you%20need%20is%20courage%20and%20support%20from%20the%20family.%E2%80%9D%20She%20is%20immensely%20grateful%20to%20her%20husband%20who%20took%20such%20good%20care%20of%20her%20down%20the%20years%2C%20without%20a%20single%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20cancer%20a%20decade%20ago.%C2%A0%20The%20couple%20has%20no%20children.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20all%20that%20she%20has%20gone%20through%2C%20she%20has%20a%20ready%20smile%20for%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayashree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMamtha%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20taught%20us%20to%20delegate%20work%20and%20encouraged%20us%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%20%E2%80%98our%20camp%E2%80%99.%20We%20all%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20this%20endeavour%20of%20hers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20after%20almost%20three%20decades%2C%20some%20of%20the%20students%20share%20their%20fond%20memories%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%20Manasa%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlways%20calm%20and%20composed%20with%20a%20smiling%20face%2C%20Sudha%20ma%E2%80%99am%20was%20the%20calm%20within%20the%20storm%20of%20kids%20at%20Siddhi%20Creations.%20She%20embodies%20Maria%20Montessori%E2%80%99s%20(an%20Italian%20educator)%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98follow%20the%20child%E2%80%99.%20She%20gave%20us%20the%20freedom%20to%20create%20and%20thrive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajath%2C%20who%20is%20an%20advocate%20today%2C%20notes%20how%20%E2%80%9CSudha%20aunty%20showered%20the%20same%20love%20on%20all%20of%20us%20and%20took%20care%20of%20all%20details%2C%20giving%20us%20the%20lesson%20of%20what%20true%20leadership%20was.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20Vijetha%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20HR%20in%20an%20MNC%2C%20Siddhi%20Creations%20and%20the%20camps%20were%20%E2%80%9Can%20important%20part%20of%20my%20childhood%2C%20in%20framing%20our%20minds%20and%20adding%20value.%E2%80%9D%20Harshith%2C%20another%20student%20of%20the%20camp%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20green%20surroundings%2C%20the%20teachers%20and%20Sudha%20ma%E2%80%99am%20with%20a%20happy%20face%20are%20unforgettable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20echoes%20these%20feelings%20when%20she%20says%20that%20it%20was%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20smile%20and%20happiness%20that%20was%20the%20best%20part%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20satisfaction%20and%20contentment%20in%20running%20the%20camps%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%20octogenarian%20from%20her%20wheelchair.%C2%A0%20Her%20voice%20is%20now%20feeble%20but%20the%20spirit%20is%20as%20strong%20as%20ever.%20There%20is%20talk%20of%20reviving%20the%20camps%20among%20the%20teachers%20who%20are%20excited%20and%20ready.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAuthored%20by%20Jayalakshmi%20Menon.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20picture%20credits%20go%20to%20Sudha%20Iyengar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698072965000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20brainchild%20of%20Sudha%20Iyengar%2C%20Siddhi%20Creations%20was%20a%20venture%20to%20keep%20young%20children%20engaged%20fruitfully%20and%20joyfully%20during%20summer%20vacations%20while%20also%20picking%20up%20on%20essential%20life%20skills.%20With%20managing%20her%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%20condition%2C%20Sudha's%20smile%20for%20everyone%20who%20enters%20her%20home%20has%20been%20winning%20hearts%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332837%2Fbengaluru-multiple-sclerosis-summer-camps-hobby-classes-sudha-iyengar-senior-citizen%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Doctor%20or%20a%20Standup%20Comedian%3F%20Dr%20Pal%20Manickam%20On%20Using%20Laughter%20As%20Medicine%20For%20Millions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHey%2C%20after%20this%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20know%20you%20inside%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Palaniappan%20Manickam%20tells%20his%20patient%20before%20doing%20an%20endoscopy%2C%20making%20the%20patient%20laugh.%20The%20gastroenterologist%2C%20based%20out%20of%20Sacramento%20in%20California%2C%20USA%2C%20uses%20humour%20to%20make%20patients%20feel%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUntil%202020%2C%20only%20his%20patients%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327134%2Fqueer-comedian-navin-noronha-on-navigating-comedy-circuit-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappreciated%20his%20humour%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20thanks%20to%20social%20media%2C%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20laughing%20with%20him.%20In%20March%202020%2C%20his%20video%20on%20COVID-19%20went%20viral%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20a%20genre%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%98Medcom%E2%80%99%20(medical%20comedy).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20positive%20response%20to%20his%20initial%20video%20led%20the%20doctor%20to%20create%20many%20videos%2C%20which%20focus%20on%20important%20medical%20topics%2C%20infused%20with%20humour%20to%20make%20them%20more%20palatable.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20around%20two%20million%20subscribers%20across%20YouTube%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20come%20to%20a%20gastroenterologist%20with%20diseases%20like%20haemorrhoids%20and%20piles%2C%20which%20they%20find%20embarrassing%20to%20describe.%20When%20patients%20have%20to%20discuss%20stool%20habits%2C%20related%20changes%2C%20acidity%20etc%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20open%20up%20right%20away.%20So%20I%20started%20breaking%20the%20ice%20using%20a%20joke.%20They%20loved%20it%2C%20so%20I%20stuck%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Pal%2C%20as%20he%20is%20fondly%20called%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20appreciation%20for%20the%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20humour%20boosted%20his%20morale%20and%20opened%20up%20doors%20for%20him%20at%20a%20standup%20comedy%20club%20in%20Bay%20Area%2C%20California%2C%20called%20%E2%80%98Building%2018%E2%80%99.%20This%20kicked%20off%20the%2039-year-old%E2%80%99s%20stint%20as%20a%20comedian.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20joined%20Building%2018%20in%20May%202020%20and%20learnt%20tips%20and%20tricks%20on%20how%20to%20write%20a%20script%2C%20how%20to%20deliver%20a%20punch%2C%20what%20is%20stand-up%20comedy%20and%20much%20more.%20I%20found%20this%20to%20be%20much%20more%20difficult%20than%20medicine%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20first%20standup%20show%20at%20the%20club%2C%20Dr%20Pal%20describes%20the%20experience%20as%20%E2%80%9Cincomparable%E2%80%9D.%20He%20says%20he%20spent%20hours%20preparing%20for%20his%2010-minute%20set%2C%20where%20he%20spoke%20about%20many%20serious%20medical%20issues%20in%20a%20comical%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20grab%20this%20chance%20that%20life%20had%20given%20him%2C%20the%20doctor%20dove%20head%20first%20into%20comedy%2C%20creating%20reels%20and%20videos%2C%20and%20doing%20shows.%20Today%2C%20he%20does%20his%20%E2%80%98medcom%E2%80%99%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20in%20the%20US%2C%20India%2C%20Malaysia%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20punchline%20for%20a%20health%20tip%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5_1yhDaDZfA%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F5_1yhDaDZfA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Dr%20Pal%20started%20his%20YouTube%20journey%20with%20a%20video%20about%20COVID%2C%20what%20really%20catapulted%20him%20to%20fame%20was%20his%20video%20on%20intermittent%20fasting%2C%20where%20he%20shared%20his%20own%20weight%20loss%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20started%20when%20the%20doctor%20had%20a%20health%20scare%20which%20made%20him%20sit%20up%20and%20take%20notice.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20100%20kg%20then%20and%20had%20palpitations%20while%20working.%20I%20realised%20how%20hypocritical%20I%20was%3B%20not%20practising%20what%20I%20was%20preaching.%20I%20had%20been%20studying%20medicine%20for%20almost%2015%20years%20but%20had%20forgotten%20to%20take%20care%20of%20my%20health%20in%20the%20process.%20I%20tried%20every%20diet%20but%20nothing%20worked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20started%20a%20research%20programme%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327558%2Frevant-himatsingka-foodpharmer-shares-how-to-read-food-labels-for-health-risks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintermittent%20fasting%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20few%20of%20his%20patients%20who%20had%20fatty%20liver.%20As%20the%20programme%20progressed%2C%20the%20doctor%20also%20started%20practising%20the%20same%20in%20his%20personal%20life.%20After%20losing%20almost%2025%20kg%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20share%20the%20lessons%20he%20learned%20with%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20had%20such%20a%20tough%20time%20losing%20weight.%20I%20wondered%20how%20tough%20it%20is%20for%20non-medical%20people.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20started%20making%20reels%20on%20Instagram%20to%20help%20people%20learn%20healthy%20habits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20delivers%20these%20important%20messages%20%E2%80%94%20about%20gut%20health%2C%20fatty%20liver%2C%20heart%20health%2C%20foods%20to%20consume%2C%20and%20tips%20for%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20comic%20element.%20To%20help%20deliver%20the%20message%20better%2C%20he%20created%20some%20imaginary%20characters%20like%20%E2%80%98Saravana%20Kumar%E2%80%99%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20like%20following%20a%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Eat%20between%20sunrise%20and%20sunset%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCt1TuJ3LM_r%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCt1TuJ3LM_r%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCt1TuJ3LM_r%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Dr.%20Pal%20Manickam%20(%40dr.pal.manickam)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Madurai-born%20doctor%20has%20advanced%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332088%2Fmugdha-pradhan-ithrive-functional-medicine-mental-health-physical-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20training%20in%20nutrition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20helps%20him%20preach%20better%20choices.%20Whereas%2C%20his%20humour%20gene%2C%20he%20says%20he%20inherited%20that%20from%20his%20father!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20shares%20that%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20help%20people%20get%20healthier%20and%20decrease%20his%20business%20by%2030%20percent%20by%202030.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20guarantee%20that%20anybody%20who%20follows%20my%20channel%20religiously%20and%20follows%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20promoting%20will%20definitely%20get%20healthier%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20people%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20lifestyle%20our%20forefathers%20were%20following%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20For%20instance%2C%20he%20suggests%20waking%20up%20early%20to%20watch%20the%20sunrise%20and%20eating%20the%20last%20meal%20before%20sunset.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20our%20ancestors%20lived%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20never%20sat%20in%20a%20single%20place.%20They%20would%20go%20out%20hunting%20for%20food%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20sun%20rose%2C%20and%20ate%20wild%20berries%2C%20tubers%20and%20fibrous%20fruits.%C2%A0%20After%20walking%20around%20the%20entire%20day%2C%20they%20would%20cook%20whatever%20they%20collected%20before%20sunset%20and%20slept%20peacefully%20due%20to%20the%20production%20of%20melatonin%2C%20which%20helps%20sleep%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20think%20how%20much%20of%20this%20is%20being%20followed%20by%20our%20generation%20today.%20The%20doctor%20jokes%20that%20his%20friend%20Saravana%20Kumar%20wakes%20up%20before%20sunrise%20only%20to%20watch%20his%20favourite%20hero%E2%80%99s%20first-day-first-show%20movie%20in%20the%20theatre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20sleeping%20two%20hours%20before%20sunrise%20these%20days!%20All%20the%20phones%20before%20bed%20neutralise%20the%20effects%20of%20melatonin%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20yo